#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is an advanced <link linkend=\"filemanager"
"\">file manager</link>, providing file management functions ranging from "
"simple cut/copy and paste operations to advanced local and remote network "
"file browsing. Folder contents can be displayed in a variety of text and "
"icon <link linkend=\"viewmode\">view modes</link>, which can include "
"thumbnail preview images of file contents. File and folder properties can "
"easily be examined and changed, and applications launched with a double "
"click of the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> je napreden <link linkend=\"filemanager"
"\">upravljalnik datotek</link>, ki zagotavlja funkcije za upravljanje "
"datotek, od preprostih operacij izrezovanja/kopiranja in lepljenja do "
"naprednega brskanja po lokalnih in oddaljenih omrežnih datotekah. Vsebina "
"mape je lahko prikazana v različnih besedilnih in ikonskih <link linkend="
"\"viewmode\">načinih prikaza</link>, ki lahko vključujejo predogledne "
"sličice vsebine datotek. Lastnosti datotek in map lahko preprosto raziščete "
"in spremenite, aplikacije pa zaženete s preprostim klikom na &LMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kde; applications, &dolphin; is the default file manager. To change the "
"default component for browsing folders, open <guimenu>Default Applications</"
"guimenu> in the &systemsettings; and select &konqueror; as file manager."
msgstr ""
"V &kde; aplikacijah je &dolphin; privzeti upravljalnik datotek. Če želite "
"spremeniti privzeto komponento za brskanje po mapah, odprite "
"<guimenu>Privzete aplikacije</guimenu> v &systemsettings; in izberite "
"&konqueror; kot upravljalnika datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is an <acronym>HTML</acronym> 5 compliant "
"<link linkend=\"browser\">web browser</link> with built-in support for "
"JavaScript (ECMA-262), <acronym>CSS</acronym> (Cascading Style Sheets) and "
"bidirectional scripts (&eg; Arabic, Hebrew and others). It provides "
"<acronym>SSL</acronym> support for secure communications. Advanced features "
"include automatic &URL; and form completion, the ability to import bookmarks "
"from other browsers and tabbed browsing."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> je skladen z <acronym>HTML</acronym> 5 "
"<link linkend=\"browser\">spletnim brskalnikom</link> z vgrajeno podporo za "
"JavaScript (ECMA-262), <acronym>CSS</acronym> (Cascading Style Sheets) in "
"dvosmerne pisave (&eg; arabščina in hebrejščina). Zagotavlja podporo za "
"varno komunikacijo <acronym>SSL</acronym>. Napredne zmožnosti vključujejo "
"samodejne &URL; in izpolnjevanje obrazcev, možnost uvoza zaznamkov iz drugih "
"brskalnikov in brskanje z zavihki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is also an excellent full featured <link "
"linkend=\"ftp\">FTP</link> client."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> je tudi odličen polni <link linkend=\"ftp"
"\">FTP</link> odjemalec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is a universal viewing application, capable "
"of displaying images and documents without having to launch another "
"application. It does this by embedding components (&kde; Parts) provided by "
"other applications; from &gwenview;; for image viewing, &okular; for "
"<acronym>PDF</acronym>, &PostScript; and other documents."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> je univerzalna aplikacija za pregledovanje, "
"ki lahko prikaže slike in dokumente, ne da bi bilo treba zagnati drugo "
"aplikacijo. To počne z vgrajevanjem komponent (&kde; Deli), ki jih "
"zagotavljajo drugi programi; od &gwenview;; za ogled slik, &okular; za "
"<acronym>PDF</acronym>, &PostScript; in druge dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is a fully customizable application which "
"anyone can <link linkend=\"config\">configure</link> to suit their own "
"needs, from changing the overall style and the sizes of text and icons to "
"selecting which items appear in the Menubar, changing the number and "
"positions of the toolbars and even defining new shortcut key combinations."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> je popolnoma prilagodljiv program, ki ga "
"lahko vsak <link linkend=\"config\">konfigurira</link> po lastnih potrebah, "
"od spreminjanja splošnega sloga ter velikosti besedila in ikon do izbire "
"elementov v meniju, spreminjanja števila in položaja orodnih vrstic ter celo "
"določanja novih kombinacij bližnjičnih tipk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; Basics"
msgstr "&konqueror; Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like all &kde; applications, &konqueror; is highly configurable. This "
"document describes how &konqueror; behaves with the normal, default settings."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot vse aplikacije &kde; je tudi &konqueror; zelo prilagodljiv. Ta "
"dokument opisuje, kako se &konqueror; obnaša pri običajnih, privzetih "
"nastavitvah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A three button mouse can be useful when you are running &konqueror; or any "
"other &kde; application. If your mouse only has two buttons then you should "
"be able to set your system up so that you can simulate a &MMB; by pressing "
"both buttons at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Miška s tremi gumbi je lahko pri uporabi &konqueror;ja ali kateregakoli "
"drugega programa &kde; zelo uporabna. Če ima vaša miška le dva gumba, potem "
"bi se moralo dati nastaviti vaš sistem tako, da lahko simulirate &MMB; s "
"hkratnim pritiskom obeh gumbov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can read more about mouse usage in <xref linkend=\"lmb-mmb\"/>"
msgstr "Več o uporabi miške si lahko preberete v <xref linkend=\"lmb-mmb\"/>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &konqueror;"
msgstr "Zagon &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the application launcher menu, select <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Internet</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Konqueror</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to start it as "
"a browser."
msgstr ""
"V meniju za zagon aplikacije izberite <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Internet</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Konqueror</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ga zaženete "
"kot brskalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> will open "
"&krunner;, enter a path to a folder and press <keysym>Enter</keysym> to "
"start in file manager mode, or just enter a &URL; such as <userinput>https://"
"www.kde.org</userinput> to start &konqueror; as a browser."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> bo odprl "
"&krunner;, vnesite pot do mape in pritisnite <keysym>Enter</keysym> za zagon "
"v načinu upravljalnika datotek ali pa samo vnesite &URL; kot je "
"<userinput>https://www.kde.org</userinput> za zagon &konqueror; kot "
"brskalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the black arrow to the right of the <guiicon>Home Page</guiicon> "
"icon to switch to your <guiicon>Home Folder</guiicon> in the file manager "
"mode and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na črno puščico na desni strani ikone <guiicon>Domača stran</"
"guiicon> preklopite na svojo <guiicon>Domača mapa</guiicon> v načinu "
"upravljalnika datotek in obratno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &konqueror; is the default file manager, it also starts automatically "
"when you double click on a desktop icon that represents a folder, such as a "
"hard disk drive or the <guiicon>Trash</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Če &konqueror; je privzeti upravljalnik datotek, se samodejno zažene tudi, "
"ko dvokliknete ikono na namizju, ki predstavlja mapo, na primer trdi disk "
"ali ikono <guiicon>Koš</guiicon>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Parts of &konqueror;"
msgstr "Deli &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "A brief look at the main parts of &konqueror;’s window:"
msgstr "Kratek pogled na glavne dele &konqueror;jevega okna:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &konqueror;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Titlebar</interface> is the strip across the top of "
"&konqueror;’s window, and operates in the same way as for other &kde; "
"applications. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the central portion "
"to bring up the neat Titlebar menu."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Naslovna vrstica</interface> je pas na vrhu &konqueror;jevega "
"okna in se obnaša podobno, kot v drugih aplikacijah &kde;. Klik z "
"<mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> gumbom miške na osrednjem delu prikliče "
"menu naslovne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Menubar</interface> is the strip containing the names of the "
"drop-down menus. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a name to "
"alternately show and hide that menu, or use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>the underlined letter</keycap></keycombo> in the name as a hot key, "
"for example <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> to "
"show the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu. The various menus are described in "
"the <link linkend=\"menubar\">Menubar</link> section of this document."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Menijska vrstica</interface> je trak, ki vsebuje imena spustnih "
"menijev. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> kliknite na ime, da izmenično "
"prikažete in skrijete ta meni, ali uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>podčrtana črka</keycap></keycombo> v imenu kot vročo tipko, na "
"primer <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> za "
"prikaz menija <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu>. Različni meniji so opisani v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"menubar\">Menijska vrstica</link> tega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Toolbar</interface> contains icons for commonly used "
"operations. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on an icon will "
"activate it. A brief description of what that icon does will appear when you "
"hover the pointer over it."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Orodna vrstica</interface> vsebuje ikone za pogosto uporabljene "
"operacije. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> klik na ikono jo aktivira. Ko se "
"s kazalcem pomaknete nad ikono, se prikaže kratek opis njenega delovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some icons, for example the Up and Back icons in the previous screenshot, "
"have a small black arrow at the right. If you click with the &LMB; at this "
"arrow a small dropdown menu will appear."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere ikone, na primer ikoni gor in nazaj na prejšnji sliki zaslona, "
"imajo na desni strani majhno črno puščico. Če kliknete z &LMB; na to "
"puščico, se prikaže majhen spustni meni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on the <interface>Toolbar</"
"interface> will bring up the <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><guilabel>Toolbar "
"Settings</guilabel> menu</link> which you can use to change the "
"<interface>Toolbar</interface>’s appearance and position."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Z desnim</mousebutton> s klikom na <interface>Orodna vrstica</"
"interface> se prikaže meni <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><guilabel>Nastavitve "
"orodne vrstice</guilabel> </link>, s katerim lahko spremenite videz in "
"položaj <interface>Orodna vrstica</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Location Toolbar</interface> shows the path to the directory, "
"&URL; or file being viewed. You can type a path or &URL; here and press "
"<keysym>Enter</keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the "
"<guiicon>Go</guiicon> icon at the right hand end of the <interface>Location "
"Toolbar</interface> to go to it. The black icon at the right hand end of the "
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> clears the text entry box."
msgstr ""
"V orodni vrstici <interface>Orodna vrstica Lokacija</interface> je prikazana "
"pot do imenika, &URL; ali datoteke, ki jo pregledujete. Tu lahko vnesete pot "
"ali &URL; in pritisnete <keysym>Enter</keysym> ali <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> kliknete ikono <guiicon>Pojdi</guiicon> na desnem koncu "
"<interface>Orodna vrstica Lokacija</interface>, da se premaknete nanjo. Črna "
"ikona na desnem koncu <interface>Orodna vrstica Lokacija</interface> počisti "
"polje za vnos besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Bookmark Toolbar</interface> is the area under the "
"<interface>Location Toolbar</interface> in the previous screenshot. You can "
"add frequently used bookmarks here; see the <link linkend=\"bookmarks"
"\">Organizing Your Bookmarks</link> section of this document."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Orodna vrstica za zaznamke</interface> je območje pod "
"<interface>Orodna vrstica Lokacija</interface> na prejšnji zaslonski sliki. "
"Sem lahko dodate pogosto uporabljene zaznamke; glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"bookmarks\">Urejanje zaznamkov</link> v tem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Window</interface> is the main area of &konqueror; and can "
"show you the contents of a directory, web page, document or image. Using the "
"<link linkend=\"menu-window\"><guimenu>Window</guimenu></link> menu you can "
"split &konqueror;’s main window into one or more separate views, useful for "
"drag and drop operations, or set it to contain two or more tabbed views."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Okno</interface> je glavno območje programa &konqueror; v njem se "
"prikaže vsebino imenika, spletne strani, dokumenta ali slike. Z menijem "
"<link linkend=\"menu-window\"><guimenu>Okno</guimenu></link> lahko glavno "
"okno programa &konqueror; razdelite na enega ali več ločenih pogledov, kar "
"je uporabno za operacije povleci in spusti, ali ga nastavite tako, da "
"vsebuje dva ali več prikazov z zavihki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Status Bar</interface> runs across the bottom of the "
"&konqueror;’s window and often shows general information about whatever the "
"mouse pointer is hovering over. If you have split the main window into a "
"number of views you will get a Status Bar for each view, and it will include "
"a small green light at the left hand end to show which is the <quote>active</"
"quote> view. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on the Status Bar "
"brings up the Status Bar <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> Mouse Button Menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Statusna vrstica</interface> poteka po dnu okna programa "
"&konqueror; in pogosto prikazuje splošne informacije o tem, nad čimer se "
"nahaja kazalec miške. Če ste glavno okno razdelili na več pogledov, boste za "
"vsak pogled dobili vrstico stanja, ki bo na levem koncu vsebovala majhno "
"zeleno lučko, ki prikazuje, kateri pogled je <quote>aktivni</quote>. "
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na vrstico stanja prikaže vrstico "
"stanja <link linkend=\"rmb-menus\"><mousebutton>Desnega</mousebutton> Menija "
"mišjega gumba</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don’t worry if your &konqueror; doesn’t look exactly like this screenshot; "
"it is highly configurable. In particular:"
msgstr ""
"Ne skrbite, če vaš &konqueror; ni videti natanko tako kot ta zaslonska "
"slika; je zelo prilagodljiv. Še zlasti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <link linkend=\"menu-settings\"><guimenu>Settings</guimenu></"
"link> menu to choose whether to show or hide the Menubar, Main Toolbar, "
"Location Toolbar and Bookmark Toolbar, or even to add an Extra Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <link linkend=\"menu-settings\"><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu></"
"link> lahko izberete, ali želite prikazati ali skriti menijsko vrstico, "
"glavno orodno vrstico, lokacijsko orodno vrstico in orodno vrstico zaznamkov "
"ali celo dodati dodatno orodno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the toolbars are unlocked, you can also drag them to a new position by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on the handle at the left hand end "
"of a bar and move it around by holding the &LMB; down while you drag it."
msgstr ""
"Če so orodne vrstice odklenjene, jih lahko tudi povlečete v nov položaj "
"tako, da <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> kliknete na ročaj na levem koncu "
"vrstice in jo premikate tako, da med vlečenjem držite &LMB; navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details of how to change &konqueror;’s appearance, see the <link "
"linkend=\"config\">Configuring &konqueror;</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti, kako spremeniti videz &konqueror;ja, si prosim poglejte "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"config\">Prilagoditev &konqueror;ja</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tooltips and What’s This?"
msgstr "Orodni namigi in Kaj je to?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find out a lot about how &konqueror; works without needing to read "
"this entire document if you take advantage of <guilabel>Tooltips</guilabel> "
"and the <guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem> feature."
msgstr ""
"Veliko informacij o tem, kako &konqueror; deluje, lahko najdete, ne da bi "
"vam bilo treba prebrati celoten dokument, če izkoristite <guilabel>Orodni "
"namigi</guilabel> in zmožnost <guimenuitem>Kaj je to?</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you hover the mouse pointer over a Toolbar tab button it should bring "
"up a terse description of what that button does."
msgstr ""
"Ko se z miškinim kazalcem pomaknete nad gumb zavihka orodne vrstice, se "
"prikaže kratek opis, kaj ta gumb počne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem> is invoked by the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> item or by <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F1</"
"keycap></keycombo>. It changes the cursor to show a question mark alongside "
"the arrow."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kaj je to?</guimenuitem> se prikliče z elementom Menijska "
"vrstica <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kaj je to?</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali z <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>. Kazalka se spremeni tako, da se ob puščici "
"prikaže vprašaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this question mark is visible, a &LMB; click won’t actually do anything "
"until you have clicked on a control (or the text alongside it) that supports "
"<guimenuitem>What’s This?</guimenuitem>, in which case it will display a "
"reasonably comprehensive description of what the control does. Most of the "
"dialog boxes that &konqueror; brings up support the <guimenuitem>What’s This?"
"</guimenuitem> feature."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta vprašaj viden, klik &LMB; dejansko ne bo naredil ničesar, dokler ne "
"kliknete na kontrolnik (ali besedilo ob njem), ki podpira <guimenuitem>Kaj "
"je to?</guimenuitem>, in v tem primeru se bo prikazal precej izčrpen opis, "
"kaj kontrolnik počne. Večina pogovornih oken, ki jih prikaže &konqueror;, "
"podpira funkcijo <guimenuitem>Kaj je to?</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>Middle</mousebutton> Mouse "
"Button Actions"
msgstr ""
"Dejanja <mousebutton>levega</mousebutton> in <mousebutton>srednjega</"
"mousebutton> gumba miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click the &LMB; on an item in &konqueror;’s window, it will be "
"<quote>activated</quote>. Thus"
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete &LMB; na element v oknu &konqueror;, se ta <quote>aktivira</"
"quote>. Tako"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an icon in the Toolbar to perform "
"the action that icon represents."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na ikono v orodni vrstici, da izvedete "
"dejanje, ki ga ta ikona predstavlja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an item in the Menubar to make that "
"menu drop down."
msgstr ""
"Klik z <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> gumbom na elementu v menujski "
"vrstici bo odprl spustni menu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a menu item to do that thing."
msgstr ""
"Klik z <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> gumbom na menujski izbiri jo bo "
"izvedel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on an icon in the Bookmark Toolbar to "
"open that &URL;."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na ikono v orodni vrstici za zaznamke, "
"da odprete ta &URL;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a link in a web page to make "
"&konqueror; follow that link."
msgstr ""
"Klik z <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> gumbom na na spletni povezavi bo "
"povzročil, da ji bo &konqueror; sledil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a folder icon or name and "
"&konqueror; will descend into (show the contents of) that folder."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na ikono ali ime mape in &konqueror; se "
"bo spustil v to mapo (prikazal njeno vsebino)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a file name or icon and &konqueror; "
"will do whatever it thinks appropriate, based on the file type. In general "
"this means opening <acronym>HTML</acronym> pages, or previewing text, image "
"or &okular; documents, showing them within &konqueror;’s window "
"(<quote>Preview</quote> means that you can see the file but not change it)."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na ime datoteke ali ikono v &konqueror; "
"bo glede na vrsto datoteke naredil, kar se mu zdi primerno. Na splošno to "
"pomeni odpiranje strani <acronym>HTML</acronym> ali predogled besedilnih, "
"slikovnih ali &okular; dokumentov, ki se prikažejo v oknu &konqueror; "
"(<quote>Predogled</quote> pomeni, da lahko vidite datoteko, vendar je ne "
"spreminjate)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; decides what the file type is by matching the filename extension "
"against a list of known types. If that fails it tries to guess the type from "
"the file contents. You can change the list of known file types and "
"associated actions with the <guilabel>File Associations</guilabel> page of "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror… "
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; se odloči, kakšna je vrsta datoteke, tako da primerja končnico "
"imena datoteke s seznamom znanih vrst. Če to ne uspe, poskuša tip uganiti iz "
"vsebine datoteke. Seznam znanih vrst datotek in z njimi povezanih dejanj "
"lahko spremenite v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Povezave datotek</guilabel> "
"strani <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"Konqueror... </guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the &MMB; on a file or folder name or icon does essentially the "
"same as <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking except that it usually does "
"it in a new &konqueror; window, unless the <guilabel>Open links in new tab "
"instead of in new window</guilabel> box has been checked in the "
"<guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem> page of the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. &konqueror; can open links on pages and "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu></menuchoice>, as well as the "
"<guibutton>Home</guibutton>, <guibutton>Up</guibutton>, <guibutton>Back</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> entries in a new tab or window."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na &MMB; na ime ali ikono datoteke ali mape naredi v bistvu enako "
"kot <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> klik, le da običajno to stori v novem "
"oknu &konqueror; razen če je polje <guilabel>Odpri povezave v novem zavihku "
"namesto v novem oknu</guilabel> označeno na strani <guimenuitem>Splošno</"
"guimenuitem> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pogovorno okno Konfiguriraj Konqueror ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. &konqueror; lahko odpira povezave na straneh in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>zaznamke</guimenu></menuchoice> ter <guibutton>Domov</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Gor</guibutton>, <guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Posreduj</guibutton> vnosa v nov zavihek ali okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding the &Shift; key down while pressing the &MMB; will open the link in "
"the background."
msgstr ""
"Če držite pritisnjeno tipko &Shift; in hkrati pritisnete &MMB;, se povezava "
"odpre v ozadju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> Mouse Button Menus"
msgstr "Menuji <mousebutton>desnega</mousebutton> gumba miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the &RMB; on almost any part of &konqueror;’s window will bring up "
"an appropriate context menu."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na &RMB; na skoraj katerem koli delu okna &konqueror; se prikaže "
"ustrezni kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the <guilabel>Right click goes back in history</"
"guilabel> option in &konqueror;’s <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> "
"configuration</link> settings a simple <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"click is equivalent to clicking on the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> button. "
"In this case you can access the context menu by moving the mouse with the "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> button held down."
msgstr ""
"Če ste omogočili možnost <guilabel>Desni klik se vrne v zgodovino</guilabel> "
"v nastavitvah <link linkend=\"othersettings\"> konfiguracije</link> "
"&konqueror;, je preprost <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> klik enak kliku na "
"gumb <guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton>. V tem primeru lahko do kontekstnega "
"menija dostopate tako, da premaknete miško s pritisnjenim gumbom "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Titlebar"
msgstr "V naslovni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on any free area of the Titlebar "
"brings up the Titlebar Menu, allowing you to control the position of "
"&konqueror;’s window as well as the decoration applied to all &kde; program "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"Klik z <mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> gumbom miške kateremkoli prostem "
"območju naslovne vrstice bo priklical meni naslovne vrstice, ki vam omogoča "
"nadzor lege &konqueror;jevega okna kot tudi dekoracije oken, ki velja za vsa "
"okna &kde; programov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Main Toolbar"
msgstr "V glavni orodni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on any free area of the Toolbar to "
"bring up the Toolbar Menu. You can also use the Toolbar Menu to set the size "
"of the buttons on the Toolbar, and whether they are shown as icons, text or "
"both."
msgstr ""
"Klik z <mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> gumbom na kateremkoli prostem "
"območju orodne vrstice bo priklical menu orodne vrstice. Uporabite ga lahko "
"za nadzor lege orodne vrstice (na vrhu, na dnu, na levi ali desni strani "
"&konqueror;jevega okna). Ta meni lahko uporabite tudi za določanje velikosti "
"gumbov v orodni vrstici in ali se naj prikažejo kot ikone, besedilo ali "
"oboje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlock the toolbar and you can move it to the top, bottom, left or right of "
"&konqueror;’s window."
msgstr ""
"Odkleni orodno vrstico in jo lahko premaknite na vrh, dno, levo ali desno od "
"okna programa &konqueror;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Location Toolbar"
msgstr "V orodni vrstici Lokacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click in the &URL; entry box area to "
"perform Cut, Copy, Paste or Clear operations in this area, or to change the "
"automatic <link linkend=\"path-complete\">Text Completion</link> features."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desna</mousebutton> kliknite na območje vnosnega polja &URL;, "
"če želite na tem območju izrezati, kopirati, prilepiti ali počistiti ali "
"spremeniti samodejne funkcije<link linkend=\"path-complete\">Dopolnjevanje "
"besedila</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Within a View"
msgstr "Znotraj pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on any free area of a view "
"then you will get a menu that contains, among other options, the "
"<guiicon>Up</guiicon>, <guiicon>Back</guiicon>, <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> "
"and <guiicon>Reload</guiicon> navigation commands."
msgstr ""
"Če <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete na katero koli prosto območje "
"pogleda, se prikaže meni, ki med drugim vsebuje navigacijske ukaze "
"<guiicon>Gor</guiicon>, <guiicon>Nazaj</guiicon>, <guiicon>Naprej</guiicon> "
"in <guiicon>Ponovno naloži</guiicon>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "On a File or Folder"
msgstr "V datoteki ali mapi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a most useful feature. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on "
"the name or icon of any file or folder not only <quote>selects</quote> that "
"item but also brings up a menu allowing you to <guimenuitem>Cut</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copy</"
"guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem> the item in various ways, "
"open it with the program of your choice or preview it, rename it, or edit "
"the file type or properties."
msgstr ""
"To je zelo uporabna funkcija. <mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na ime "
"ali ikono katere koli datoteke ali mape ne le <quote>izbere</quote> ta "
"element, temveč prikaže tudi meni, ki omogoča <guimenuitem>izrezati</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>premakniti</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>kopirati</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>odstraniti</guimenuitem> element na različne "
"načine, odpreti ga z izbranim programom ali predogledom, preimenovati ali "
"urediti vrsto ali lastnosti datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the Status Bar"
msgstr "Na statusni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the Status Bar at the bottom of a "
"window or view to add or remove a view and lock or link views within "
"&konqueror;’s window."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na vrstico stanja na dnu okna ali "
"pogleda, da dodate ali odstranite pogled in zaklenete ali povežete poglede "
"znotraj okna &konqueror;ja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Help, Man and Info Pages"
msgstr "Pregledovanje strani pomoči, priročnika in informacijskih strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can view &kde; Help and &UNIX; Man and Info pages directly in "
"&konqueror;, without having to start up &khelpcenter;."
msgstr ""
"Pomoč &kde; ter strani &UNIX; Man in Info si lahko ogledate neposredno v "
"programu &konqueror;, ne da bi vam bilo treba zagnati program &khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view a &kde; Help page, enter <userinput>help:/<replaceable>application "
"name</replaceable></userinput> (for example <userinput>help:/"
"<replaceable>kmail</replaceable></userinput> to view the &kmail; "
"documentation.) into &konqueror;’s Location Toolbar window."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled &kde; Strani s pomočjo, vnesite <userinput>help:/<replaceable>ime "
"aplikacije</replaceable></userinput> (na primer <userinput>help:/"
"<replaceable>kmail</replaceable></userinput> za ogled dokumentacije "
"&kmail;.) v okno orodne vrstice lokacije &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to read &UNIX; Man pages &konqueror; makes it easy. For example "
"type <userinput>man:/touch</userinput> or <userinput>#touch</userinput> into "
"the Location Toolbar to see the page for the <command>touch</command> "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Če želite brati &UNIX; strani Man, vam &konqueror; to olajša, vtipkajte na "
"primer <userinput>man:/touch</userinput> ali pa <userinput>#touch</"
"userinput> v lokacijsko vrstico, da si ogledate navodila za ukaz "
"<command>touch</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To browse through &UNIX; Info pages, entering <userinput>info:/dir</"
"userinput> takes you to Info’s top level directory, then it’s just a matter "
"of clicking on the right links to find the page you want. Alternatively, use "
"<userinput>info:/<replaceable>command name</replaceable></userinput> to go "
"straight to the Info page you want."
msgstr ""
"Če želite brskati po straneh &UNIX; Info, vas vnos <userinput>info:/dir</"
"userinput> pripelje v imenik Info na najvišji ravni, nato pa je treba le še "
"klikniti na prave povezave, da najdete želeno stran. Uporabite tudi "
"<userinput>info:/<replaceable>imena ukazov</replaceable></userinput>, da "
"greste naravnost na želeno informacijsko stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, &kde; Help pages are stored in such a way that they cannot be "
"viewed in other browsers. If you really need to do this your only recourse "
"is to go online and visit <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org\"> http://docs."
"kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Na žalost so strani pomoči shranjene tako, da jih ni mogoče pregledati v "
"drugih brskalnikih. Če to res morate storiti, je vaša edina možnost, da "
"obiščete splet <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org\"> http://docs.kde.org</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; the File Manager"
msgstr "&konqueror; upravljalnik datotek"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders and Paths"
msgstr "Mape in poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &UNIX; and &Linux; all folders are arranged in a simple hierarchy. "
"Starting from a top level folder (also called the root directory), the "
"structure descends and branches containing various files and subfolders. "
"This means that you can get from any folder to any other by going <quote>up "
"</quote> until you reach a common point then <quote>down</quote> through the "
"appropriate subfolders until you reach your target."
msgstr ""
"V sistemih &UNIX; in &Linux; so vse mape urejene v preprosti hierarhiji. "
"Struktura se začne z mapo najvišje ravni (imenovano tudi korenski imenik), "
"nato pa se začne spuščati in se razveji z različnimi datotekami in "
"podmapami. To pomeni, da lahko iz katere koli mape v katero koli drugo "
"pridete tako, da greste <quote>gor </quote>, dokler ne dosežete skupne "
"točke, nato <quote>dol</quote> skozi ustrezne podmape, dokler ne dosežete "
"cilja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The position of any file or folder in the structure (also called a directory "
"tree) can be described by its <quote>path</quote>, which is a simple list of "
"the folders you would have to descend through to get to the target folder or "
"file. For example <filename class=\"directory\">/home/pam</filename> is the "
"subfolder <filename class=\"directory\">pam</filename> of the subfolder "
"<filename class=\"directory\">home</filename> of the top level folder, and "
"<filename>/home/pam/words.txt</filename> is the file <filename>words.txt </"
"filename> in that subfolder. The leading <quote>/</quote> in these paths "
"represents the top level folder."
msgstr ""
"Položaj datoteke ali imenika v drevesu se lahko opiše z njegovo "
"<quote>potjo</quote>, ki je preprost seznam imenikov, preko katerih bi "
"morali, da bi prišli v ciljni imenik. Na primer: <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/dom/pam</filename> je podimenik <filename class=\"directory\">pam</"
"filename> podimenika <filename class=\"directory\">dom</filename> vrhnjega "
"nivoja, ki ga predstavlja <quote>/</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every folder accessible by your system &mdash; including those on other hard "
"disk partitions, a USB device or &CD-ROM; &mdash; will appear in the tree "
"descending from /, their exact paths will depend on how your system was set "
"up (see also the section on <link linkend=\"removable-devices\">Removable "
"Devices</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Vse mape, ki so dostopne sistemu, vključno s tistimi na drugih particijah "
"trdega diska, napravi USB ali &CD-ROM; &mdash;, se bodo prikazale v drevesu, "
"ki se spušča od /, njihove natančne poti pa so odvisne od tega, kako je bil "
"sistem nastavljen (glejte tudi poglavje <link linkend=\"removable-devices"
"\">Odstranljive naprave</link>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every user on a &UNIX; / &Linux; system has their own <quote>home</quote> "
"folder to hold their personal files and settings; for example <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/home/john</filename> and <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"home/mary</filename>. The symbol <keycap>~</keycap> is often used to "
"represent the user’s home folder, so that <filename>~/letter.txt</filename> "
"refers to the file <filename>letter.txt</filename> in my home folder."
msgstr ""
"Vsak uporabnik v sistemu &UNIX; / &Linux; ima svojo mapo <quote>dom</quote>, "
"v kateri hrani svoje osebne datoteke in nastavitve; na primer <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/home/john</filename> in <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"home/mary</filename>. Simbol <keycap>~</keycap> se pogosto uporablja za "
"predstavitev uporabnikove domače mape, tako da se <filename>~/pismo.txt</"
"filename> nanaša na datoteko <filename>pismo.txt</filename> v moji domači "
"mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the term <quote>directory</quote> is often used instead of "
"<quote>folder</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se namesto izraza <quote>imenik</quote> pogosto uporablja "
"izraz <quote>mapa</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes"
msgstr "Načini prikaza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In File Manager mode, &konqueror; lists which files and subfolders are "
"contained within a given folder and can provide you with some information "
"about them. The <quote>path</quote> of the current folder is shown in the "
"Location Toolbar. The way that &konqueror; displays the files and folders "
"depends mainly on your choice of view mode which can be selected from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> sub menu. The view modes &konqueror; provides are outlined below."
msgstr ""
"V načinu upravljalnika datotek &konqueror; prikaže, katere datoteke in "
"podmape so v določeni mapi, in vam lahko o njih posreduje nekaj informacij. "
"<quote>pot</quote> trenutne mape je prikazana v orodni vrstici Lokacija. "
"Način, na katerega &konqueror; prikazuje datoteke in mape, je odvisen "
"predvsem od izbire načina prikaza, ki ga lahko izberete v podmeniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Način prikaza</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>. Načini pogleda, ki jih omogoča &konqueror;, so opisani spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In File Manager mode, &konqueror; uses an embedded &dolphin; component. "
"Please refer to the &dolphin; documentation for detailed information about "
"this mode."
msgstr ""
"V načinu upravljalnika datotek &konqueror; uporablja vdelan &dolphin; "
"komponento. Oglejte si &dolphin; dokumentacijo za podrobne informacije o tem "
"načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Icons</guibutton> view, which is the default, files will "
"be represented by an icon that visualizes the file type, and a folder icon "
"will be shown for subfolders. The names of folders and files, and the items "
"enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional "
"Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, are displayed below the icons."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu <guibutton>Ikone</guibutton>, ki je privzet, bodo datoteke "
"predstavljene z ikono, ki ponazarja vrsto datoteke, za podmape pa bo "
"prikazana ikona mape. Pod ikonami so prikazana imena map in datotek ter "
"elementi, omogočeni v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Compact</guilabel> view shows the folder contents as icons "
"with the name beside it and the items enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice> below "
"the name. The items are grouped in columns similar to the <guilabel>Short "
"View</guilabel> in the &kde; file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Kompaktni</guilabel> prikazuje vsebino mape kot ikone z "
"imenom poleg in elementi, omogočenimi v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</guisubmenu></menuchoice> pod "
"imenom. Elementi so razvrščeni v stolpce, podobno kot <guilabel>Kratek "
"pogled</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu &kde; datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Details</guibutton> view, the folder contents are "
"displayed as a detailed list which contains the name, size and last "
"modification time of each item. Additional columns can be added by clicking "
"a column header with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu <guibutton>Podrobnosti</guibutton> je vsebina mape prikazana kot "
"podroben seznam, ki vsebuje ime, velikost in čas zadnje spremembe vsakega "
"elementa. Dodatne stolpce lahko dodate tako, da kliknete na glavo stolpca z "
"znakom &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the context menu of the header line you can choose between custom or "
"automatic column width. Automatic width adjusts the width of all columns "
"once to display the longest item in the column completely, except for the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel> column where the extension is replaced by <quote>…"
"</quote>"
msgstr ""
"V kontekstnem meniju naslovne vrstice lahko izbirate med širino stolpca po "
"meri ali samodejno. Samodejna širina enkrat prilagodi širino vseh stolpcev, "
"da v celoti prikaže najdaljši element v stolpcu, razen stolpca "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, kjer je pripona nadomeščena z <quote>…</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The order of columns can be changed by drag and drop of column headers, "
"except for the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> header, which is always the first "
"column in this view."
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red stolpcev lahko spreminjate z vlečenjem in spuščanjem glave "
"stolpcev, razen glave <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, ki je v tem pogledu vedno "
"prvi stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The details view allows you to view the current directory in a tree-like "
"fashion if <guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel> are enabled: Each "
"subfolder of the current folder can be <quote>expanded</quote> or "
"<quote>collapsed</quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> or "
"<guiicon>v</guiicon> icon next to it."
msgstr ""
"Pogled podrobnosti omogoča prikaz trenutnega imenika na drevesni način, če "
"je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Razširljive mape</guilabel>: vsako podmapo "
"trenutne mape lahko <quote>razširite</quote> ali <quote>skrčite</quote> s "
"klikom na ikono <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> ali <guiicon>v</guiicon> poleg nje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Grouped View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skupinski pogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Grouped View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skupinski pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All view modes support grouping by the sort type selected in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sort by</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Vsi načini prikaza podpirajo razvrščanje v skupine glede na vrsto "
"razvrščanja, izbrano v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrsti po</guisubmenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information in the View"
msgstr "Informacije v pogledu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all view modes &konqueror; shows at least an icon and a name for each "
"item. Using <guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu> in the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu or the context menu of the header in "
"<guilabel>Details</guilabel> mode, you can select more information for each "
"item to be shown:"
msgstr ""
"V vseh načinih prikaza &konqueror; prikaže vsaj ikono in ime za vsak "
"element. Z uporabo <guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</guisubmenu> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> ali v kontekstnem meniju glave v načinu "
"<guilabel>Podrobnosti</guilabel> lahko izberete več informacij za vsak "
"prikazan element:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Size</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Date</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Type</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Rating</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Tags</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Velikost</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Datum</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Tip</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Ocena</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Oznake</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the file type, additionally, the following criteria can be "
"selected:"
msgstr "Glede na vrsto datoteke lahko dodatno izberete naslednje kriterije:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Document</guimenuitem>: Number of words and lines"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Dokument</guimenuitem>: Število besed in vrstic"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Image</guimenuitem>: Size and orientation"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Slika</guimenuitem>: Velikost in usmerjenost"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Audio</guimenuitem>: Artist, album, duration and track"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Zvok</guimenuitem>: izvajalec, album, trajanje in skladba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guisubmenu>Other</guisubmenu> submenu allows to select "
"<guimenuitem>Path</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Link Destination</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copied From</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Owner</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>User Group</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"V podmeniju <guisubmenu>Drugo</guisubmenu> lahko izberete <guimenuitem>Pot</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Cilj povezave</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kopirano iz</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Dovoljenja</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Lastnik</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Skupina "
"uporabnikov</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder View Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti pogleda mape"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following settings control how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"the &konqueror; view, and are stored on a per-folder basis by default:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje nastavitve določajo, kako je vsebina mape prikazana v pogledu "
"&konqueror; in so privzeto shranjene za posamezno mapo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "The view mode (Icons, Compact, Details)"
msgstr "Način pogleda (Ikone, Kompaktno, Podrobnosti)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sorting of items, which is determined by the sort order (ascending, "
"descending) and the attribute (such as name, size, …) that the items are "
"sorted by"
msgstr ""
"Razvrščanje elementov, ki je določeno z vrstnim redom (naraščajoče, "
"padajoče) in atributom (kot so ime, velikost, ...), po katerem so elementi "
"razvrščeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting of folders and files &ndash; are folders shown first or not?"
msgstr "Razvrščanje map in datotek &ndash; so mape prikazane prve ali ne?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Previews &ndash; are they shown instead of icons (based on the settings made "
"in <guilabel>Previews</guilabel> tab of &konqueror;’s General settings) or "
"not?"
msgstr ""
"Predogledi &ndash; ali so prikazani namesto ikon (na podlagi nastavitev v "
"zavihku <guilabel>Predogledi</guilabel> v splošnih nastavitvah programa "
"&konqueror;) ali ne?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are items shown in groups in the views?"
msgstr "Ali so elementi v prikazih prikazani v skupinah?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are hidden files shown?"
msgstr "Ali so prikazane skrite datoteke?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What additional information (besides the name) is shown in the Icons or "
"Details view?"
msgstr ""
"Katere dodatne informacije (poleg imena) so prikazane v pogledu Ikone ali "
"Podrobnosti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view properties can be configured in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu></menuchoice> menu, some (such as the view mode) can also be changed "
"using toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"Lastnosti pogleda lahko nastavite v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu></menuchoice>, nekatere (na primer način pogleda) pa lahko "
"spremenite tudi z gumbi orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Properties Dialog"
msgstr "Lastnosti pogleda pogovornega okna"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the View Properties dialog"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika pogovornega okna Lastnosti pogleda"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Properties dialog."
msgstr "Lastnosti pogleda pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Properties Dialog."
msgstr "Lastnosti pogleda pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View Properties</guilabel> dialog can be used to quickly "
"modify several view properties at once. This is done for the current folder, "
"for the current folder including all subfolders, or even for all folders, "
"depending on the choice made in the <guilabel>Apply View Properties To</"
"guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"S pogovornim oknom <guilabel>Oglejte si lastnosti</guilabel> lahko hitro "
"spremenite več lastnosti pogleda hkrati. To se izvede za trenutno mapo, za "
"trenutno mapo z vsemi podmapami ali celo za vse mape, odvisno od izbire v "
"razdelku <guilabel>Uporabi Lastnosti pogleda za</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Use these view properties as default</guilabel> is enabled, the "
"chosen view properties will also be used for all folders which do not have "
"customized view properties yet."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Te lastnosti pogleda uporabite kot "
"privzete</guilabel>, bodo izbrane lastnosti pogleda uporabljene tudi za vse "
"mape, ki še nimajo prilagojenih lastnosti pogleda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get to a file with &konqueror; you first need to navigate through the "
"folder tree to find the folder containing that file."
msgstr ""
"Če želite priti do datoteke s programom &konqueror; morate najprej krmariti "
"po drevesu map in poiskati mapo, ki vsebuje to datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "To move between folders you can simply step up and down the tree:"
msgstr ""
"Da se premikate med imeniki, se preprosto sprehodite navzgor in navzdol po "
"drevesu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To descend into a subfolder <mousebutton>left </mousebutton> click on its "
"name or icon —or if you have already <quote>selected</quote> it (see below)— "
"then just press <keysym>Enter</keysym>."
msgstr ""
"Za spust v podmapo <mousebutton>leva </mousebutton> kliknite njeno ime ali "
"ikono - ali če ste jo že <quote>izbrali</quote> (glejte spodaj) - nato "
"pritisnite <keysym>Enter</keysym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To go up the folder tree you can click on the <guiicon>Up</guiicon> button "
"in the Toolbar, use<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></"
"keycombo>, or use the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"Če želite iti navzgor po drevesu map, lahko v orodni vrstici kliknete na "
"gumb <guiicon>Gor</guiicon>, uporabite<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>Gor</keysym></keycombo> ali uporabite možnost menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Gor</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <quote>select</quote> a file or folder in the displayed folder without "
"opening it in any way use the <keysym>up</keysym> and <keysym>down </keysym> "
"arrow keys to move through the items. The selected item will be highlighted "
"and some information about it will be displayed in the Status Bar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <quote>izbrati</quote> datoteko ali mapo v prikazani mapi, ne da "
"bi jo kakor koli odprli, uporabite puščične tipke <keysym>gor</keysym> in "
"<keysym>dol</keysym> za premikanje po elementih. Izbrani element bo označen, "
"v vrstici stanja pa bodo prikazane nekatere informacije o njem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Setting the <link linkend=\"viewmode\">View Mode</link> to <guimenuitem> "
"Details</guimenuitem> can help you locate folders in the tree below the "
"current folder; in this mode each folder is shown with a small box at the "
"left. If the box contains a <keycap>&gt;</keycap> sign, <mousebutton>left </"
"mousebutton> clicking on the box (not on the folder name or icon) will "
"display a sub tree showing files and subfolders contained in that folder. "
"The small box will then change to show a <keycap>v</keycap> sign. "
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on that to collapse the sub tree. Once "
"you have found the folder you are looking for, <mousebutton>left </"
"mousebutton> click on the folder name or icon to open it."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev <link linkend=\"viewmode\">Način pogleda</link> na <guimenuitem> "
"Podrobnosti</guimenuitem> vam lahko pomaga pri iskanju map v drevesu pod "
"trenutno mapo; v tem načinu je vsaka mapa prikazana z majhnim poljem na "
"levi. Če polje vsebuje znak <keycap>&gt;</keycap>, bo <mousebutton>levi </"
"mousebutton> klik na polje (ne na ime mape ali ikono) prikazal pod drevo, ki "
"prikazuje datoteke in podmape v tej mapi. Majhno polje se nato spremeni in "
"prikaže znak <keycap>v</keycap>. <mousebutton>Leva</mousebutton> kliknite "
"nanj, da se pod drevo zruši. Ko najdete želeno mapo, <mousebutton>levo </"
"mousebutton> kliknite ime mape ali ikono, da jo odprete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can go directly to any folder by switching with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Location</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap> </"
"keycombo> to the Location Bar and typing its path. &konqueror;’s <link "
"linkend=\"path-complete\"> Text Completion</link> feature may be useful when "
"you do this. Don’t forget that in &Linux; / &UNIX; file and folder names are "
"case sensitive."
msgstr ""
"Lahko greste neposredno v katero koli mapo tako, da preklopite z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri lokacijo</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>O</"
"keycap> </keycombo> v lokacijsko vrstico in vtipkate njeno pot. Funkcija "
"<link linkend=\"path-complete\"> Dopolnjevanje besedila</link> &konqueror;ja "
"je morda uporabna, ko to storite. Ne pozabite, da v &Linux; / &UNIX; so "
"imena datotek in map občutljiva glede velikih in malih črk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have moved to a new folder you can go back to your previous choice "
"by using the Toolbar <guiicon>Back</guiicon> button, the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> item, or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Left</keysym></"
"keycombo>. Once you have gone back you can go forward. Use the Toolbar "
"<guiicon>Forward</guiicon> button, the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem></menuchoice> item or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Ko se premaknete v novo mapo, se lahko vrnete na prejšnjo izbiro z gumbom "
"orodne vrstice <guiicon>Nazaj</guiicon>, elementom menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Levo</keysym></"
"keycombo>. Ko se vrnete nazaj, lahko greste naprej. Uporabite gumb orodne "
"vrstice <guiicon>Naprej</guiicon>, element menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Naprej</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Desno</keysym></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can also choose to enter the parent folder by clicking on "
"the Toolbar <guiicon>Up</guiicon>, the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem></menuchoice> item, or with <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"V matično mapo lahko vstopite tudi tako, da kliknete orodno vrstico "
"<guiicon>Gor</guiicon>, element <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Gor</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali s <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keysym>Gor</keysym></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the checkmark at the right of the toolbar <guiicon>Up</guiicon>, "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> buttons or selecting "
"these items in the <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu brings up a submenu of "
"recently visited locations."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na kljukico na desni strani gumbov orodne vrstice <guiicon>Gor</"
"guiicon>, <guiicon>Nazaj</guiicon> ali <guiicon>Naprej</guiicon> ali izbiro "
"teh elementov v meniju <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> se prikaže podmeni nedavno "
"obiskanih lokacij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files and Folders"
msgstr "Iskanje datotek in map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don’t know or can’t remember where a file or folder is within your "
"system, then use the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo> or the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find File…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. This "
"starts the file finder application &kfind;. See the <ulink url=\"help:/kfind/"
"index.html\">&kfind; Handbook</ulink> for help in using &kfind;."
msgstr ""
"Če ne veste ali se ne morete spomniti, kje je datoteka ali mapa v vašem "
"sistemu, uporabite bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo> ali možnost menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi datoteko…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. S tem se "
"zažene program za iskanje datotek &kfind;. Oglejte si <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kfind/index.html\">&kfind; Priročnik</ulink> za pomoč pri uporabi &kfind;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the name of a file or folder begins with a period (dot), then it is a "
"<quote>hidden</quote> file or folder, and will not normally be shown by "
"&konqueror;. To see hidden files or folders use the Menubar <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hidden Files</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Če se ime datoteke ali mape začne s piko, je to <quote>skrita</quote> "
"datoteka ali mapa in je program &konqueror; običajno ne prikaže. Za prikaz "
"skritih datotek ali map uporabite možnost Menijska vrstica <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Skrite datoteke</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another reason &konqueror; may not show the file or folder you are looking "
"for is that you may have the <link linkend=\"konq-plugin\"><guilabel> "
"Directory Filter</guilabel></link> plugin set to display only certain types "
"of file."
msgstr ""
"Drugi razlog, zakaj &konqueror; morda ne bo prikazal datoteke ali mape, ki "
"jo iščete, je, da imate morda vtičnik <link linkend=\"konq-plugin"
"\"><guilabel> Filtriranje imenikov</guilabel></link> nastavljen tako, da "
"prikazuje samo določene vrste datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removable Devices"
msgstr "Odstranljive naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any removable device (USB stick, &CD; drive or other hard disk partition "
"that you have on your system) will usually appear in the <filename class="
"\"directory\">/</filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/media</filename>, "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/mnt</filename> or <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/auto</filename> folder, having a path something like <filename class="
"\"directory\">/mnt/floppy</filename> or <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"cdrom</filename>. The details will depend on how your system was set up."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka odstranljiva naprava (ključek USB, &CD; pogon ali druga particija "
"trdega diska, ki jo imate v sistemu) bo običajno prikazana v mapi <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/</filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/media</"
"filename>, <filename class=\"directory\">/mnt</filename> ali <filename class="
"\"directory\">/auto</filename>, s potjo, podobno <filename> class=\"directory"
"\">/mnt/floppy</filename> ali <filename class=\"directory\">/cdrom</"
"filename>. Podrobnosti bodo odvisne od tega, kako je bil vaš sistem "
"nastavljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; / &Linux; requires that you <command>mount</command> a removable "
"device when you have inserted it into the drive, and <command>mount </"
"command> other hard disk partitions when you want to access them. You also "
"need to unmount a removable device before removing it to register that it is "
"no longer available."
msgstr ""
"&UNIX; / &Linux; zahteva, da <command>namesti</command> odstranljivo "
"napravo, ko jo vstavite v pogon, in <command>namesti</command> druge "
"particije trdega diska, ko želite do njih dostopati. Pred odstranitvijo "
"odstranljive naprave jo morate tudi odmestiti, da se zabeleži, da ni več na "
"voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "How you do this will depend on your system setup:"
msgstr "Kako to naredite, je odvisno od nastavitve vašega sistema:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the <guilabel>Device Notifier</guilabel>"
msgstr "Uporaba <guilabel>Obveščevalnika naprav</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a &kde; session the <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-desktop/index.html#device-"
"notifier\">Device Notifier</ulink> window will popup, when you insert a "
"removable device and allows you to select an appropriate application for "
"this media or only mount the device."
msgstr ""
"V seji &kde; se ob vstavitvi izmenljive naprave prikaže okno <ulink url="
"\"help:/plasma-desktop/index.html#device-notifier\">Obveščevalnik naprav</"
"ulink>, ki omogoča izbiro ustrezne aplikacije za ta medij ali samo "
"namestitev naprave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use the <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> layout for your desktop, you "
"may have icons for removable devices on your desktop, in which case &LMB; "
"click on the icon to mount it. Doing this should also bring up a &konqueror; "
"window showing the contents of the device. To unmount, <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on the icon and choose the <guimenuitem>Unmount</"
"guimenuitem> item. Visit the section <link linkend=\"making\">Create New…</"
"link> in this Handbook to see how to create such an icon."
msgstr ""
"Če za namizje uporabljate postavitev <guilabel>Pogled map</guilabel>, imate "
"na namizju morda ikone za izmenljive naprave, v tem primeru &LMB; kliknite "
"na ikono, da ga namestite. S tem bi se moral prikazati tudi okno "
"&konqueror;, ki prikazuje vsebino naprave. Za odpenjanje <mousebutton>z "
"desnim gumbom</mousebutton> kliknite ikono in izberite element "
"<guimenuitem>Odpni</guimenuitem>. Obiščite razdelek <link linkend=\"making"
"\">Ustvari novo…</link> v tem priročniku in si oglejte, kako ustvariti "
"takšno ikono."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or you can do it the traditional way by typing into a text console window:"
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa se tega lotite na tradicionalen način, tako da v terminalsko okno "
"vtipkate:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount /mnt/floppy"
msgstr "mount /mnt/floppy"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "to mount, for example, the floppy drive, and"
msgstr "za namestitev, na primer disketnega pogona, in"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "umount /mnt/floppy"
msgstr "umount /mnt/floppy"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to unmount it (<command>umount</command> not <command>unmount</command>)."
msgstr ""
"da ga odklopite. Vtipkajte <command>umount</command>, ne <command>unmount</"
"command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than having to open a text console to type the <command>mount </"
"command> or <command>umount</command> commands, you may prefer to use "
"&konqueror;’s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell "
"Command</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) feature."
msgstr ""
"Namesto, da bi odprli tekstovno konzolo in vtipkali vanjo ukaza "
"<command>mount </command> ali <command>umount</command>, lahko uporabite "
"&konqueror;jevo možnost <menuchoice><guimenu> Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvedba ukaza Shell</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting Files and Folders"
msgstr "Brisanje datotek in map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; gives you two ways to dispose of an unwanted file or folder:"
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; vam ponuja dva načina za odstranitev nezaželenih datotek ali map:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move it to the <filename>Trash</filename> folder, which is the "
"safest method as you can get it back if you realize that you have made a "
"mistake."
msgstr ""
"Lahko jih premaknete v imenik <filename>Smeti</filename>, kar je najvarnejša "
"metoda, saj jih lahko povrnete, kadar ugotovite, da ste naredili napako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can just plain Delete it, which removes the entry from the folder and "
"adds the disk area occupied by the file(s) to the system’s list of free disk "
"areas, in the same way as the <command>rm</command> command."
msgstr ""
"Lahko jo preprosto izbrišete, kar odstrani vnos iz mape in doda območje "
"diska, ki ga zasedajo datoteke, na sistemski seznam prostih območij diska na "
"enak način kot ukaz <command>rm</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to use this feature check the option <guilabel>Show “Delete” "
"menu entries which bypass the trashcan</guilabel> on the <guilabel>File "
"Management</guilabel> settings page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabljati to zmožnost, na strani z nastavitvami <guilabel>Prikaz "
"vnosov menija \"Izbriši\", ki obidejo koš za smeti</guilabel> preverite "
"možnost nastavitev <guilabel>Upravljanje datotek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The simplest way to remove a file or folder is to position the mouse pointer "
"over its name or icon and press the &RMB;, which will bring up a menu "
"containing the options <guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteko ali mapo najenostavneje odstranite tako, da postavite kazalec miške "
"nad njeno ime ali ikono in pritisnete &RMB;, s čimer se prikaže meni z "
"možnostma <guimenuitem>Premakni v koš</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Odstrani</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or, if you have <quote>selected</quote> the item, the Menubar <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> menu will give you the choice of <quote><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</"
"guimenuitem></quote> and <quote><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem></quote> "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Če ste <quote>izbrali</quote> element, lahko v meniju Menubar "
"<guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu> izberete možnosti <quote><guimenuitem>Premakni v "
"koš</guimenuitem></quote> in <quote><guimenuitem>Odstrani</guimenuitem></"
"quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Del</keycap> will move the selected item or items to Trash."
msgstr "<keycap>Del</keycap> bo premaknil izbran element ali elemente v Smeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> will "
"really, truly and irrevocably delete the selected item or items."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Del</keycap></"
"keycombo> bo resnično in nepovratno izbrisal izbran(e) element(e)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You won’t be able to remove a file or folder if you don’t have the necessary "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke ali mape ne boste mogli odstraniti, če nimate potrebnih dovoljenj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving and Copying"
msgstr "Premikanje in prepisovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "To copy a file or subfolder between folders you can:"
msgstr "Če želite kopirati datoteko ali podmapo med mapami, lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Position the mouse pointer over its name or icon and hold down the &RMB;, "
"which will bring up a menu containing the <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> "
"option. Choose that."
msgstr ""
"Postavite kazalko miške nad imenom ali ikono in držite &RMB;, ki bo "
"priklical meni, ki bo vseboval izbiro <guimenuitem>Prepiši</guimenuitem>. "
"Izberite jo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Or if the item is <quote>selected</quote> you can use the <guiicon>Copy</"
"guiicon> button on the Toolbar or the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice> item, or the <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> shortcut key "
"combination. You can also select <link linkend=\"selection\">multiple</link> "
"files or folders to copy/move as well."
msgstr ""
"Če je element <quote>izbran</quote> lahko uporabite gumb <guiicon>Kopiraj</"
"guiicon> v orodni vrstici ali pa izbiro v menijski vrstici "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali pa kombinacijo tipk <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</"
"keycap><keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>. Izberete lahko tudi <link linkend="
"\"selection\">več</link> datotek ali map za kopiranje/premikanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate to the folder you want to copy the item into then Paste the item "
"into the new folder by using the Toolbar <guiicon>Paste</guiicon> button or "
"the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or by moving the mouse pointer to a "
"clear area of the window and holding the &RMB; down to bring up a menu "
"containing the <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> option."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v mapo, v katero želite kopirati element, nato element prilepite v "
"novo mapo z gumbom <guiicon>Prilepi</guiicon> v orodni vrstici ali z "
"možnostjo <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski vrstici ali z bližnjico <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> ali s premikom kazalca "
"miške na prosto območje okna in držanjem &RMB; navzdol za prikaz menija z "
"možnostjo <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving a file or subfolder between folders can be done in the same way as "
"copying, except that you choose the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> option or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> instead of "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>. The item that you have <guimenuitem>Cut</"
"guimenuitem> will be removed from the original folder when you do the "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> into the new folder."
msgstr ""
"Premikanje datoteke ali podmape med mapami lahko izvedete na enak način kot "
"kopiranje, le da namesto možnosti <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> "
"izberete možnost <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem> ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>. Element, ki ste ga "
"<guimenuitem>izrezali</guimenuitem>, bo odstranjen iz prvotne mape, ko "
"opravite <guimenuitem>prilepite</guimenuitem> v novo mapo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Drag’n Drop"
msgstr "Uporaba povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; also supports Drag and Drop copying and moving of files and "
"folders."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; podpira tudi kopiranje in premikanje datotek in map s funkcijo "
"povleci in spusti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can do this by having two instances of &konqueror;, one showing the "
"folder you want to copy from, the other showing the target folder. Position "
"the mouse pointer over the item you wish to copy or move, then, holding the "
"&LMB; pressed, <quote>drag</quote> it to a clear space in the target folder. "
"Release the button and you will be presented with a menu choice of "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Here</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move Here</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Link Here</guimenuitem>. Take care to <quote>drop</quote> "
"the item into an empty area of the target folder view—dropping it on top of "
"a subfolder will copy or move the item into that folder."
msgstr ""
"To lahko storite tako, da imate dva pojavka &konqueror;ja, pri čemer eden "
"prikazuje mapo, iz katere želite kopirati, drugi prikazuje ciljno mapo. "
"Kazalec miške postavite nad element, ki ga želite kopirati ali premakniti, "
"nato pa držite &LMB; pritisnete, ga <quote>povlecite</quote> na prazen "
"prostor v ciljni mapi. Spustite gumb in v meniju se vam bo prikazala izbira "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj sem</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Premakni sem</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Povezava sem</guimenuitem>. Pazite, da "
"<quote>spustite</quote> element v prazno območje pogleda ciljne mape – če ga "
"spustite na vrh podmape, boste element kopirali ali premaknili v to mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also set up &konqueror; to show more than one folder within its "
"window and drag &amp; drop between them."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko tudi &konqueror; da v svojem oknu prikaže več kot eno mapo "
"in jo povlečete &amp; spustite med njimi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split Views for Drag &amp; Drop"
msgstr "Razdeli pogled za 'povleci in spusti'"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This screenshot illustrates the use of the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Left/Right</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, also available with the shortcut <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>, to split the "
"main &konqueror; window into two views, each showing the contents of a "
"different folder."
msgstr ""
"Ta zaslonska slika prikazuje uporabo možnosti menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razdeljeni pogled levo/"
"desno</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki je na voljo tudi z bližnjico <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>, za razdelitev "
"glavnega okna &konqueror; na dva pogleda, pri čemer vsak prikazuje vsebino "
"druge mape."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be able to show different folders in each view they should not be linked; "
"the little boxes at the bottom right of each view should be empty."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati različne mape v vsakem pogledu, te ne smejo biti "
"povezane; majhna polja na spodnji desni strani vsakega pogleda morajo biti "
"prazna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>active</quote> view, that is the one whose path is shown in the "
"Location Toolbar and which responds to navigation and Menubar commands, is "
"shown by the little green light in the bottom left corner. To make a view "
"active, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on an empty area of the view "
"or on its Status Bar."
msgstr ""
"<quote>aktivni</quote> pogled, torej tisti, katerega pot je prikazana v "
"orodni vrstici Lokacija in ki se odziva na ukaze navigacije in menijske "
"vrstice, je prikazan z majhno zeleno lučko v spodnjem levem kotu. Če želite "
"prikaz narediti aktiven, <mousebutton>leva</mousebutton> kliknite na prazno "
"območje prikaza ali na njegovo vrstico stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an active view from &konqueror;’s window use the <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> shortcut, or the "
"Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close Active View</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, or &RMB; click on the Status Bar and "
"choose the <guimenuitem>Close View</guimenuitem> option from the resulting "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti aktivni pogled iz okna &konqueror;, uporabite bližnjico "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> ali "
"možnost menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Okno</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri aktivni pogled</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"&RMB; kliknite statusno vrstico in izberite možnost <guimenuitem>Zapri "
"pogled</guimenuitem> iz menija, ki se prikaže."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use &konqueror; tabs, you can drag and drop between tabs by dragging "
"the file to the tab label, without letting go yet. The destination tab will "
"pop to the front, allowing you to continue dragging and then to drop the "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate zavihke &konqueror;, lahko datoteke med zavihki povlečete "
"tako, da datoteko povlečete na oznako zavihka, ne da bi jo izpustili. "
"Kartica cilja se bo prikazala na sprednji strani, tako da boste lahko "
"nadaljevali z vlečenjem in nato spustili datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Duplicate File or Folder Names"
msgstr "Podvoji imena datotek ali map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to paste a file or folder into a folder that already contains an "
"item with the same name, &konqueror; will pop up a dialog box warning you "
"that the item already exists. You can then choose to:"
msgstr ""
"Če poskušate prilepiti datoteko ali mapo v mapo, ki že vsebuje element z "
"istim imenom, se prikaže pogovorno okno z opozorilom, da element že obstaja. "
"Nato lahko izberete:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cancel the paste operation by pressing the <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Prekličite postopek lepljenja s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give the item that is being copied a different name. You can do this by "
"typing a new name into the text entry box or get &konqueror; to "
"<guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton>. When you have done this press the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Predelu, ki ga kopiramo, dajte drugo ime. To lahko storite tako, da v polje "
"za vnos besedila vnesete novo ime ali pa uporabite &konqueror; za "
"<guibutton>Predlagaj novo ime</guibutton>. Ko to storite, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have copied multiple items, <guibutton>Skip</guibutton> the current "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Če ste kopirali več elementov, <guibutton>Preskoči</guibutton> trenutni "
"element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Apply to All</guibutton> button can be used if you have "
"copied multiple items."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Uporabi za vse</guibutton> lahko uporabite, če ste kopirali "
"več elementov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items in the View"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov v pogledu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several ways to select items in the view. Once a group of items is "
"selected, all actions, such as <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and drag "
"and drop operations, affect all selected items."
msgstr ""
"Elemente v pogledu lahko izberete na več načinov. Ko je izbrana skupina "
"elementov, vsa dejanja, kot so <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izreži</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Premakni v koš</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ter operacije povleci in spusti, vplivajo na vse izbrane "
"elemente."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov z miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around a "
"group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items in "
"the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
"pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
msgstr ""
"Nekje v pogledu lahko pritisnete &LMB; in narišete pravokotnik okoli skupine "
"elementov, preden spustite gumb. S tem izberete vse elemente v pravokotniku "
"in izbrišete prejšnji izbor. Če med izbiranjem pritisnete tipko &Shift;, se "
"ohrani prejšnja izbira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, the "
"selection state of this item is toggled. If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while "
"a rectangle is drawn around a group of items as described above, the "
"selection state of all items in the rectangle will be toggled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Ctrl;, medtem ko je element kliknjen z &LMB;, se "
"spremeni stanje izbire tega elementa. Če pritisnete tipko &Ctrl; med "
"risanjem pravokotnika okoli skupine elementov, kot je opisano zgoraj, se "
"spremeni stanje izbire vseh elementov v pravokotniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, all "
"items between the previous current item and the clicked item will be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Shift;, medtem ko kliknete element z &LMB;, bodo "
"izbrani vsi elementi med prejšnjim trenutnim elementom in kliknjenim "
"elementom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov s tipkovnico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an arrow key, <keysym>PgUp</keysym>, <keysym>PgDn</keysym>, <keycap>Home</"
"keycap>, or <keycap>End</keycap> is pressed, the new current item is "
"selected, and the previous selection is cleared."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete puščično tipko, <keysym>PgUp</keysym>, <keysym>PgDn</keysym>, "
"<keycap>Dom</keycap> ali <keycap>Konec</keycap>, je izbrana nova trenutna "
"postavka, prejšnja izbira pa je izbrisana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, the "
"selection remains unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Če med pritiskom ene od zgornjih tipk držite tipko &Ctrl;, izbira ostane "
"nespremenjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, all items "
"between the previous current item and the new current item will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Če med pritiskom ene od zgornjih tipk držite tipko &Shift;, bodo izbrani vsi "
"elementi med prejšnjim trenutnim elementom in novim trenutnim elementom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> is "
"pressed, the selection state of the current item is toggled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></"
"keycombo>, se spremeni stanje izbire trenutnega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> selects all "
"items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> izbere vse "
"elemente v pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"toggles the selection state of all items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"preklopi stanje izbire vseh elementov v pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and the "
"first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and cancel the "
"keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of 1 second."
msgstr ""
"Datoteko ali mapo izberete tako, da vnesete prvih nekaj črk njenega imena in "
"izbran je prvi ustrezni element. Če želite izbrisati izbiro in preklicati "
"iskanje po tipkovnici, pritisnite &Esc; ali počakajte dlje od 1 sekunde."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Menu"
msgstr "Izbira elementov z uporabo menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You sometimes want to delete, copy or move a number of files that are "
"similar in some way. For example you may wish to move all of the <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.png</filename> graphics files from one folder to "
"another. &konqueror; makes this easy by letting you select multiple files "
"based on similarities in their file names."
msgstr ""
"Včasih želite izbrisati, kopirati ali premakniti več datotek, ki so si na "
"nek način podobne. Morda boste na primer želeli premakniti vse grafične "
"datoteke <filename class=\"extension\">.png</filename> iz ene mape v drugo. "
"&konqueror; to olajša, saj vam omogoča, da izberete več datotek na podlagi "
"podobnosti imen datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select Matching Items…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"option or the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo>. This brings up a little dialog box in which you enter a filename "
"containing the wildcard characters <keycap>*</keycap>, which matches any "
"number of characters, and <keycap>?</keycap> which matches a single "
"character. Press <guibutton>OK</guibutton> and &konqueror; will highlight "
"all files with matching names. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite možnost menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izbor</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi ujemajoče se "
"elemente…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>. Prikaže se majhno pogovorno okno, v "
"katerega vnesete ime datoteke, ki vsebuje nadomestne znake <keycap>*</"
"keycap>, ki ustreza poljubnemu številu znakov, in <keycap>?</keycap>, ki "
"ustreza enemu samemu znaku. Pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> in "
"&konqueror; bo označil vse datoteke z ujemajočimi se imeni. Na primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><filename>flag*.png</filename></userinput> will select all "
"filenames starting with the letters <quote>flag</quote> and ending with "
"<quote><literal role=\"extension\">.png</literal></quote>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><filename>zastava*.png</filename></userinput> bo izbral vse "
"datoteke, katerih ime se prične s črkami <quote>zastava</quote> in konča z "
"<quote><filename>.png</filename></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><filename>memo?.txt</filename></userinput> will select "
"<filename>memo1.txt</filename> and <filename>memo9.txt</filename> but not "
"<filename>memo99.txt</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><filename>memo?.txt</filename></userinput> bo izbral "
"<filename>memo1.txt</filename> in <filename>memo9.txt</filename> vendar pa "
"ne <filename>memo99.txt</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have selected a range of files, you can narrow down the selection "
"by using the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect Matching "
"Items…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option to specify which of the selected "
"files should be removed from the selection."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste izbrali vrsto datotek, lahko izbor zožite tako, da z možnostjo "
"Menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izbira</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izloči ujemajoče predmete...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> določite, katere od izbranih datotek naj se odstranijo iz izbora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect All</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or "
"just &LMB; click on a clear area of the view to cancel the selection."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite možnost Menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izbor</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prekliči vse</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali preprosto &LMB; kliknite na prosto območje "
"pogleda, da prekličete izbor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can even invert the selection: that is, deselect all selected files and "
"select those that were previously unselected. Use the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Invert Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> to "
"do this."
msgstr ""
"Izbiro lahko celo obrnete: to pomeni, da razveljavite izbiro vseh izbranih "
"datotek in izberete tiste, ki prej niso bile izbrane. Za to uporabite "
"možnost Menijske vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izbor</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Obrni izbor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create New"
msgstr "Ustvari nov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &konqueror; is in File Manager mode, picking <guisubmenu>Create New</"
"guisubmenu> from &RMB; clicking on a free area in a folder view gives you a "
"submenu letting you create any of the following in the current folder:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je &konqueror; v načinu upravljalnika datotek, z izbiro možnosti "
"<guisubmenu>Izdelaj novo</guisubmenu> v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> ali "
"v kontekstnem meniju, ki ga dobite s &RMB; klikom na prosto območje v "
"pogledu mape, dobite podmeni, ki vam omogoča ustvarjanje katerega od "
"naslednjih elementov v trenutni mapi:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder…"
msgstr "Mapa…"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid "An easy way of creating a new (sub)folder."
msgstr "Preprost način za ustvarjanje novih (pod)map."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text File…"
msgstr "Besedilna datoteka..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this to create an ordinary, empty, text file. A dialog box will be "
"opened for you to enter the name of your new file."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ga za ustvarjanje navadne, prazne besedilne datoteke. Odprlo se bo "
"pogovorno okno, v katerega boste lahko vnesli ime nove datoteke."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid "HTML File…"
msgstr "Datoteka HTML..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a skeleton <acronym>HTML</acronym> source file. When you type the "
"new file’s name into the dialog box it is probably best to give it a "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.html </literal> extension to avoid confusion."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari ogrodje <acronym>HTML</acronym> datoteke. Ko vnesete ime nove "
"datoteke v majhno pogovorno okno, je najbolje, da ji dodate končnico "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.html</literal>, da se izognete zmedi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>Type of Document</replaceable> Document…"
msgstr "<replaceable>Vrst dokumenta</replaceable> Dokument..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the installed applications and file associations several "
"menuitems for different types of documents are displayed and enable you to "
"create skeleton documents of the selected type."
msgstr ""
"Glede na nameščene aplikacije in združenja datotek se prikaže več menijskih "
"elementov za različne vrste dokumentov, ki omogočajo ustvarjanje ogrodnih "
"dokumentov izbrane vrste."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link to Location (URL)…"
msgstr "Povezava na lokacijo (URL)..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you create an icon to open &konqueror; at a particular folder or "
"web page. As with <guimenuitem>Link To Application…</guimenuitem> you can "
"make the application icon appear on your desktop by creating the link in "
"your <filename>~/Desktop</filename> folder or going to the "
"<guisubmenu>Create New…</guisubmenu> sub menu by right clicking on a free "
"area of the desktop."
msgstr ""
"S tem lahko ustvarite ikono za odprtje programa &konqueror; v določeni mapi "
"ali spletni strani. Tako kot pri <guimenuitem>Povezava na aplikacijo...</"
"guimenuitem> lahko ikono aplikacije prikažete na namizju tako, da ustvarite "
"povezavo v mapi <filename>~/Namizje</filename> ali v podmeniju "
"<guisubmenu>Ustvari novo...</guisubmenu> z desnim klikom na prosto območje "
"namizja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link to File or Directory…"
msgstr "Povezava do datoteke ali imenika..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a symbolic link for local files or folder."
msgstr "Ustvarite simbolično povezavo za lokalne datoteke ali mapo."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Link to Application…"
msgstr "Povezava do aplikacije..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is most useful if you want to create an icon that will open a "
"particular application. It opens a dialog box with several tabbed pages. The "
"first, <guilabel>General</guilabel>, is where you choose an icon and the "
"text that will appear with it. The second page, <guilabel>Permissions</"
"guilabel>, lets you select who can use or modify the icon. In the "
"<guilabel>Application</guilabel> page you must enter the <guilabel>Command</"
"guilabel> that will run the application, for example, <userinput>kwrite</"
"userinput> to start up the &kwrite; text editor. <userinput>kwrite /home/pam/"
"todo.txt</userinput> would open the file <filename>/home/pam/todo.txt</"
"filename> in &kwrite;. Advanced options such as the file types which the "
"application can open are also available from this page."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je najbolj uporabna, če želite ustvariti ikono, ki bo odprla "
"določeno aplikacijo. Odpre se pogovorno okno z več stranmi z zavihki. V "
"prvem, <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>, izberete ikono in besedilo, ki bo "
"prikazano z njo. Na drugi strani, <guilabel>Dovoljenja</guilabel>, lahko "
"izberete, kdo lahko uporablja ali spreminja ikono. Na strani "
"<guilabel>Aplikacija</guilabel> morate vnesti <guilabel>Ukaz</guilabel>, ki "
"bo zagnal aplikacijo, na primer <userinput>kwrite</userinput> za zagon "
"urejevalnika besedila &kwrite;. <userinput>kwrite /dom/pam/todo.txt</"
"userinput> bi odprl datoteko <filename>/dom/pam/todo.txt</filename> v "
"&kwrite;. Na tej strani so na voljo tudi napredne možnosti, kot so vrste "
"datotek, ki jih lahko aplikacija odpre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the application icon appear on your desktop, create the link in your "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/Desktop</filename> folder (this may be "
"called something slightly different depending on how &kde; was installed on "
"your system) or get to the <guisubmenu>Create New…</guisubmenu> sub menu by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on a free area of the desktop "
"instead of within &konqueror;’s window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se ikona programa prikaže na namizju, ustvarite povezavo v "
"mapi <filename class=\"directory\">~/Namizje</filename> (ta se lahko imenuje "
"nekoliko drugače, odvisno od tega, kako je bil &kde; nameščen v vaš sistem) "
"ali pridite do podmenija <guisubmenu>Ustvari Nov...</guisubmenu> tako, da z "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete prost prostor na namizju namesto v "
"oknu &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a lot of specialized application links and don’t want to clutter "
"up the desktop, then why not create them in your Applications folder. You "
"can get there in &konqueror; by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Applications</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then create a single "
"icon on your desktop to open your Applications folder, which is usually in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/applications</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate veliko posebnih povezav do aplikacij in ne želite, da bi bile na "
"namizju nepregledne, jih ustvarite v mapi Aplikacije. Do tja lahko pridete v "
"programu &konqueror; z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Aplikacije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato na namizju "
"ustvarite eno samo ikono za odpiranje mape Aplikacije, ki je običajno v "
"<filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share/applications</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To put an application link icon into the panel, first create it in the "
"Applications folder then drag the icon onto a clear area of the panel."
msgstr ""
"Če želite na ploščo namestiti ikono povezave do aplikacije, jo najprej "
"ustvarite v mapi Aplikacije, nato pa povlecite ikono na prosto območje na "
"plošči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Names and Permissions"
msgstr "Spreminjanje imen in dovoljenj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two easiest ways to change the name of a file or folder is to either "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on it and select <guimenuitem>Rename</"
"guimenuitem>, or select the file or folder and then press the <keycap>F2</"
"keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Ime datoteke ali mape lahko najlažje spremenite tako, da <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> kliknete nanjo in izberete <guimenuitem>Ponovno poimenuj</"
"guimenuitem> ali izberete datoteko ali mapo in pritisnete tipko <keycap>F2</"
"keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name or permissions of a file or folder <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on its name or icon and select the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item, or if you have <quote>selected</"
"quote> the file or folder, then you can use the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo>) option."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ime ali dovoljenja datoteke ali mape "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknite njeno ime ali ikono in izberite "
"element <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> ali če ste <quote>izbrali</"
"quote> datoteko ali mapo, lahko uporabite možnost Menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Vrni</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will bring up the Properties dialog box with several tabbed pages:"
msgstr "To prikaže pogovorno okno Lastnosti z več zavihki:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>General</guilabel>, which gives you some information about the "
"item and lets you change its name and, for a folder, the associated icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>, ki vam da nekaj podatkov o elementu in vam "
"omogoča spreminjanje njegovega imena in za mapo, tudi privzete ikone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel>, which shows you the item’s ownership and "
"access permissions and lets you change the permissions."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dovoljenja</guilabel>, ki vam prikaže lastništvo elementa in "
"dovoljenja za dostop, omogoča pa tudi spreminjanje dovoljenj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and Rename"
msgstr "Kopiranje in preimenovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to make a copy of an existing file with a different name —"
"perhaps as a backup— in the same folder as the original file, do a normal "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> then when you <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> it a dialog box will pop up, complaining that the file already "
"exists. Just type the new name into the dialog’s text box and press the "
"<guibutton>Continue</guibutton> button (or if you are feeling lazy pressing "
"the <guibutton>Suggest New Name</guibutton> button will generate a new name "
"for you)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narediti kopijo obstoječe datoteke z drugačnim imenom - morda kot "
"varnostno kopijo - v isti mapi kot izvirno datoteko, naredite običajen "
"postopek <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>, nato pa se ob "
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> prikaže pogovorno okno s pritožbo, da "
"datoteka že obstaja. Samo vnesite novo ime v besedilno polje pogovornega "
"okna in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Nadaljuj</guibutton> (ali če ste leni, "
"pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Predlagaj novo ime</guibutton> in ustvarite novo "
"ime namesto vas)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring File Associations"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje povezav datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kde; provides many applications which can open many different types of "
"file. Most of the time, the defaults will work with no problems, but "
"&konqueror; provides a powerful system to allow you to change the "
"applications used to open each file type. For more details, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, select <guilabel>File Associations</"
"guilabel> in the configuration dialog, and click on <guibutton>Help</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"&kde; ponuja veliko aplikacij, ki lahko odprejo veliko različnih vrst "
"datotek. Večinoma bodo privzete nastavitve delovale brez težav, vendar "
"&konqueror; ponuja zmogljiv sistem, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje aplikacij, "
"ki se uporabljajo za odpiranje posameznih vrst datotek. Če želite več "
"podrobnosti, izberite meni <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Konquerorja...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"izberite <guilabel>Povezave datotek</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu za "
"konfiguracijo in kliknite <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid "At the Command Line"
msgstr "V ukazni vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although &konqueror; is a very powerful and flexible <acronym>GUI</acronym> "
"file manager, there are occasions when the experienced &Linux; / &UNIX; user "
"wants to get down to the basics and work at the text command line level."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je &konqueror; zelo zmogljiv in prilagodljiv <acronym>GUI</acronym> "
"upravljalnik datotek, se zgodi, da se izkušeni &Linux; / &UNIX; uporabnik "
"želi posvetiti osnovam in delati na ravni ukazne vrstice za besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can, of course, open an instance of &konsole;, perhaps with "
"&konqueror;’s Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open "
"Terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option or with <keycap>F4</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Seveda lahko odprete pojavek &konsole;, morda z možnostjo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri Terminal</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v meniju &konqueror; ali z <keycap>F4</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only want to launch a program or view a &URL;, the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) "
"option may be easier."
msgstr ""
"Če želite le zagnati program ali si ogledati &URL;, je morda lažja možnost "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvrši ukaz lupine...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Execute Shell Command… </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo>) opens a small command line dialog window where you can "
"enter a shell command such as <userinput>ps -ax | grep kdeinit </userinput>. "
"Note that it does not support full featured terminal control characters, so "
"applications such as <userinput>top</userinput> and <userinput> less</"
"userinput> will not work properly, but it is available immediately without "
"the delay involved in starting &konsole;."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvrši ukaz lupine... </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>E</"
"keycap></keycombo>) odpre majhno pogovorno okno ukazne vrstice, v katero "
"lahko vnesete ukaz lupine, na primer <userinput>ps -ax | grep kdeinit </"
"userinput>. Upoštevajte, da ne podpira vseh znakov za nadzor terminala, zato "
"aplikacije, kot sta <userinput>top</userinput> in <userinput> less</"
"userinput>, ne bodo delovale pravilno, vendar je na voljo takoj, brez zamude "
"pri zagonu &konsole;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more complex operations, &konqueror; has another nice feature: the "
"Menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Terminal "
"Emulator</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option, which opens up a terminal window "
"as a new view within &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Za bolj zapletene operacije ima &konqueror; še eno lepo funkcijo: možnost "
"Menijska vrstica <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži emulator terminala</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"ki odpre okno terminala kot nov pogled v &konqueror;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Including the terminal emulator"
msgstr "Vključevanje terminalskega emulatorja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; the Web Browser"
msgstr "&konqueror; - spletni brskalnik"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing www.konqueror.org"
msgstr "Brskanje www.konqueror.org"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Surfing and Searching"
msgstr "Brskanje in iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have a connection to the Internet, you can surf with &konqueror; "
"just as you can with any other browser."
msgstr ""
"Ko vzpostavite povezavo z internetom, lahko brskate z &konqueror; tako kot s "
"katerim koli drugim brskalnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type a &URL; into the Location Toolbar window, press <keysym>Enter</keysym> "
"or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-jump.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> <guibutton>Go</"
"guibutton> button at the right hand end of the Location Toolbar, and "
"&konqueror; will download and display that page. If you have visited the "
"page before, &konqueror;’s <link linkend=\"path-complete\">Automatic Text "
"Completion</link> feature can help you type the &URL; a second time. If you "
"want to use one of the web’s search engines, &konqueror;’s Web Search "
"Keywords feature can make this easier."
msgstr ""
"V okno lokacijske orodne vrstice vnesite &URL;, pritisnite <keysym>Enter</"
"keysym> ali <mousebutton>leva</mousebutton> kliknite "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"go-jump.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> <guibutton>Go</"
"guibutton> gumb na desnem koncu lokacijske orodne vrstice in &konqueror; bo "
"prenesel in prikazal to stran. Če ste stran že obiskali, vam lahko funkcija "
"<link linkend=\"path-complete\">Samodejno dokončanje besedila</link> v "
"programu &konqueror; pomaga pri ponovnem vnosu naslova &URL;. Če želite "
"uporabiti enega od spletnih iskalnikov, vam to lahko olajša funkcija <link "
"linkend=\"enhanced-browsing\"> Spletne bližnjice</link> v programu "
"&konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on a link in a page to open that link."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Leva</mousebutton> kliknite povezavo na strani, da jo odprete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open a link in a new instance of &konqueror;, leaving the old page still "
"visible, &RMB; click on the link and select the <guimenuitem>Open in New "
"Window</guimenuitem> option. Alternatively, you might want to "
"<guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem>. <link linkend=\"tabbrowse"
"\">Tabbed Browsing</link> will let you hold a number of pages in one "
"&konqueror; window and quickly switch between them with a single mouse click."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti povezavo v novem primerku programa &konqueror;, pri čemer "
"je stara stran še vedno vidna, kliknite povezavo in izberite možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri v novem oknu</guimenuitem>. Druga možnost je "
"<guimenuitem>Odprite v novem zavihku</guimenuitem>. <link linkend=\"tabbrowse"
"\">Prehajanje po zavihkih</link> vam omogoča, da imate več strani v enem "
"oknu in hitro preklapljate med njimi z enim klikom miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could also select multiple view modes with <menuchoice><guimenu>Window</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Left/Right</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>) / "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split View Top/Bottom</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>) option which will let you see different pages "
"at the same time. This can be useful if you are looking through a "
"complicated set of <acronym>HTML</acronym> pages, but make sure the little "
"link box at the bottom right hand corner is empty when you are doing this."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi več načinov prikaza z možnostjo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razdeljeni pogled Leva/"
"Desna</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;"
"<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>) / <menuchoice><guimenu>Okno</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razdeljeni pogled Zgornji/spodnji del</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo>), s katero si boste hkrati lahko ogledali različne strani. To je "
"lahko koristno, če pregledujete zapletene strani <acronym>HTML</acronym>, "
"vendar pri tem poskrbite, da bo majhno polje za povezave v spodnjem desnem "
"kotu prazno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To go back to the previous page use the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>Left</keysym></keycombo> shortcut, the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> "
"button on the Toolbar, or the menubar <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite vrniti na prejšnjo stran, uporabite bližnjico <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Leva</keysym></keycombo>, gumb <guibutton>Nazaj</"
"guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali možnost menijske vrstice "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, once you have gone back you can go forward by using <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></keycombo>, the "
"<guibutton>Forward</guibutton> button, or the menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"Podobno lahko po vrnitvi nazaj nadaljujete naprej z uporabo <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Desna</keysym></keycombo>, gumba <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton> ali možnosti menijske vrtsice <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are multiple ways of scrolling the viewing area. One is to use the "
"<keysym>Up</keysym> and <keysym>Down</keysym> keys. You may also use the "
"scrollbar, your mousewheel or the <keysym>PgUp</keysym> and <keysym>PgDn</"
"keysym> keys."
msgstr ""
"Območje za ogled lahko pomikate na več načinov. Ena je uporaba tipk "
"<keysym>Gor</keysym> in <keysym>Dol</keysym>. Uporabite lahko tudi vrstico "
"za pomikanje, kolesce miške ali tipki <keysym>PgUp</keysym> in <keysym>PgDn</"
"keysym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to stop a download for any reason then use the &Esc; key, the "
"Toolbar <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> button or the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prenos iz kakršnega koli razloga ustaviti, uporabite tipko &Esc;, "
"gumb <guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali element menijske "
"vrstice <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are viewing a web page with the <guilabel>HTML Toolbar</guilabel> "
"enabled you should see two new icons in the toolbar "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"format-font-"
"size-less.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> and <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"format-font-size-more.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>. Use these to adjust the size of the text in "
"the page if you find it difficult to read. How well this works will depend "
"on how the web page has been constructed."
msgstr ""
"Ko si ogledate spletno stran z omogočeno orodno vrstico <guilabel>HTML "
"Orodna vrstica</guilabel>, morate v orodni vrstici videti dve novi ikoni "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"format-font-"
"size-less.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> in <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"format-font-size-more.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>. Z njimi lahko prilagodite velikost besedila na "
"strani, če ga težko berete. Kako dobro bo to delovalo, je odvisno od načina "
"izdelave spletne strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabbed Browsing"
msgstr "Brskanje z zavihki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using this feature you can make &konqueror; load multiple web pages in "
"the same window, and switch between them using tabbed pages. This way, you "
"can preload a page <quote>in the background</quote> while you carry on "
"reading another."
msgstr ""
"S to funkcijo lahko v istem oknu naložite več spletnih strani in med njimi "
"preklapljate z zavihki. Na ta način lahko vnaprej naložite stran <quote>v "
"ozadju</quote>, medtem ko nadaljujete z branjem druge strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use tabbed browsing, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a link and "
"choose <guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem> from the drop down menu or "
"&MMB; click. The page will be downloaded and displayed as normal, but with "
"tabs across the top of the view, one tab for each page. &LMB; click on a tab "
"to view that page, or you can use the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> to cycle through the tab pages. Alternatively, "
"you can scroll through the tabs using the mouse <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton> while the mouse pointer is over the tab bar (presuming that "
"your mouse has one). Also, double-clicking over the empty tab bar space will "
"open a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti brskanje z zavihki, <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknite povezavo in izberite <guimenuitem>Odpri v novem zavihku</"
"guimenuitem> v spustnem meniju ali &MMB; kliknite. Stran bo prenesena in "
"prikazana kot običajno, vendar z zavihki na vrhu pogleda, po en zavihek za "
"vsako stran. &LMB; kliknite zavihek za ogled te strani ali pa uporabite "
"bližnjici <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> in "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> za premikanje "
"po straneh zavihkov. Druga možnost je, da se po zavihkih pomikate z miškinim "
"<mousebutton>kolesce</mousebutton>, ko je kazalec miške nad vrstico zavihkov "
"(če jo miška ima). Z dvojnim klikom na prazen prostor v vrstici zavihkov "
"boste odprli nov zavihek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guilabel>Open new tabs in the background</guilabel> option in the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> page of the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> dialog, "
"clicking on a link downloads the page and shows a new tab for it, but the "
"new page will not be displayed until you <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click on the tab."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo možnosti <guilabel>Odpri nov zavihek v ozadju</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> pogovornega okna <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"klik na povezavo prenese stran in zanjo prikaže nov zavihek, vendar se nova "
"stran ne prikaže, dokler <mousebutton>leva</mousebutton> ne kliknete zavihka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Open links in new tab instead of in new window</"
"guilabel> box in the <guimenuitem>General</guimenuitem> page of the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror… </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog, &MMB; clicking on a link will open it in a "
"new tab page and if you hold the &Shift; key down while clicking the &MMB; "
"the link will be opened in a background tab page."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Odprite povezave v novem zavihku namesto v novem "
"oknu</guilabel> na strani <guimenuitem>Splošno</guimenuitem> pogovornega "
"okna <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"Konqueror... </guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se bo &MMB; s klikom na povezavo "
"odprla na strani z novim zavihkom in če med klikom &MMB; držite tipko "
"&Shift; pritisnjeno, se povezava odpre na strani z zavihkom ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a tab will bring up a menu with "
"the following options:"
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na zavihek prikaže meni z naslednjimi "
"možnostmi:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>New Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Nov zavihek</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens a new, blank, tabbed page view. You can then download a web page "
"into it by typing the &URL; into the Location Bar or by making a selection "
"from the Bookmark Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Odpre se nov, prazen prikaz strani z zavihki. Spletno stran lahko vanj "
"prenesete tako, da v lokacijsko vrstico vnesete &URL; ali izberete v orodni "
"vrstici za zaznamke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Podvajanje zavihka</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a duplicate tabbed page."
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje podvojene strani z zavihki."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Reload Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Znova naloži zavihek</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the content of the current tab."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži vsebino trenutnega zavihka."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Tabs"
msgstr "Drugi zavihki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a submenu showing all other tabs. Choosing a tab from this list "
"makes it the active tab."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže podmeni z vsemi drugimi zavihki. Če izberete zavihek s tega seznama, "
"postane aktivni zavihek."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Other Tabs</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Reload All Tabs</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F5</"
"keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Drugi zavihki</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Osveži vse "
"zavihke</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the content of every tab."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži vsebino vsakega zavihka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guisubmenu>Other Tabs</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Close Other Tabs</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guisubmenu>Drugi zavihki</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Zapri druge zavihke</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "To close all but the selected tab page."
msgstr "Za zapiranje vseh zavihkov razen izbranega."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Detach Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odklop zavihka</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option removes the selected tabbed page from the current &konqueror; "
"window and opens it in a new instance of &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost odstrani izbrano stran z zavihki iz trenutnega okna &konqueror; "
"in jo odpre v novem primeru &konqueror;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Close Tab</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zapri zavihek</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid "To close the selected tab page."
msgstr "Če želite zapreti stran izbranega zavihka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Search Keywords"
msgstr "Ključne besede spletnega iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &konqueror;’s Web Search Keywords feature lets you submit a "
"query directly to a search engine or similar web site without having to "
"visit the site first."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, vam &konqueror;jeva funkcija Ključne besede za spletno "
"iskanje omogoča predložitevpoizvedbe neposredno v iskalniku ali podobni "
"spletni strani, ne da bi vam bilo treba najprej obiskati stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, entering <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput> into the Location "
"Bar and pressing <keysym>Enter</keysym> will ask <trademark>Google</"
"trademark> to search for items related to &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Če na primer v lokacijsko vrstico vpišete <userinput>gg:konqueror</"
"userinput> in pritisnete <keysym>Enter</keysym>, bo <trademark>Google</"
"trademark> zahteval iskanje elementov, povezanih s &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see what Web Search Keywords are available, and perhaps add your own, "
"open the <guilabel>Web Search Keywords</guilabel> page in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti, katere ključne besede spletnega iskanja so na voljo, in "
"morda dodati svoje,odprite stran <guilabel>Ključne besede spletnega iskanja</"
"guilabel> na strani <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Konqueror…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access Keys"
msgstr "Ključi za dostop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has full support for the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</"
"sgmltag> &HTML; attribute in forms and links. Access keys allow you to use "
"the keyboard keys for functions which would perhaps normally be done with "
"the mouse, such as following links. The benefit of this is, quite simply, "
"that users can interact with a page with devices other than a pointing "
"device."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; ima popolno podporo za atribut <sgmltag class=\"attribute"
"\">accesskey</sgmltag> &HTML; v obrazcih in povezavah. Tipke za dostop "
"omogočajo uporabo tipk na tipkovnici za funkcije, ki bi jih običajno "
"opravili z miško, na primer sledenje povezavam. Prednost tega je preprosto "
"ta, da lahko uporabniki s stranjo komunicirajo tudi z drugimi napravami, ne "
"le s kazalkami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature has to be enabled by checking the <guilabel>Enable Access Key "
"activation with &Ctrl; key</guilabel> option on the <guilabel>Web Browsing</"
"guilabel> settings page."
msgstr ""
"To funkcijo je treba omogočiti tako, da na strani z nastavitvami "
"<guilabel>Vključi aktivacijo dostopnega ključa s tipko &Ctrl;</guilabel> "
"preverite možnost <guilabel>Brskanje po spletu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the access keys in &konqueror;, press and release &Ctrl;. Once "
"this is pressed, if a particular link on the website has the <sgmltag class="
"\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> attribute in the given link, then the "
"character(s) should appear over the link, identifying what needs to be "
"pressed. Then, you can enter the character(s) associated with the link as an "
"alternative to following the link with the mouse. To disable the access keys "
"once activated you can press &Ctrl; again."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati tipke za dostop v programu &konqueror;, pritisnite in "
"sprostite &Ctrl;. Ko je ta pritisnjena, se, če ima določena povezava na "
"spletnem mestu atribut <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> v "
"dani povezavi, nad povezavo prikažejo znaki, ki določajo, kaj je treba "
"pritisniti. Nato lahko namesto sledenja povezavi z miško vnesete znak(-e), "
"povezan(-e) s povezavo. Če želite onemogočiti enkrat aktivirane tipke za "
"dostop, lahko znova pritisnete &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The proper use of this feature requires that the web designer of the page "
"has specifically assigned, using the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</"
"sgmltag> attribute, an access key for the link. Many web designers might not "
"include the <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> in their links "
"and forms, and consequently this feature will be unusable on the given "
"webpage."
msgstr ""
"Za pravilno uporabo te funkcije mora oblikovalec spletne strani s pomočjo "
"atributa <sgmltag class=\"attribute\">accesskey</sgmltag> posebej dodeliti "
"ključ dostopa za povezavo. Številni oblikovalci spletnih strani morda v "
"svoje povezave in obrazce ne bodo vključili <sgmltag class=\"attribute"
"\">accesskey</sgmltag>, zato te funkcije na določeni spletni strani ne bo "
"mogoče uporabljati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browser Identification"
msgstr "Identifikacija brskalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &konqueror; connects to a web site it sends some brief browser "
"identification information, known as the <quote>User Agent</quote> string. "
"Many web sites use this information to customize the pages that they send "
"back, based on the strengths and weaknesses of different browsers."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &konqueror; poveže s spletnim mestom, pošlje nekaj kratkih "
"identifikacijskih podatkov brskalnika, znanih kot niz <quote>Uporabniški "
"agent</quote>. Številna spletna mesta te informacije uporabljajo za "
"prilagajanje strani, ki jih pošiljajo nazaj, glede na prednosti in slabosti "
"različnih brskalnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, some badly designed sites refuse to work properly unless you "
"are using a browser that the site recognizes as a <quote>valid</quote> one, "
"even though if given a chance, &konqueror; will work satisfactorily with the "
"vast majority of web pages."
msgstr ""
"Na žalost nekatera slabo zasnovana spletna mesta ne delujejo pravilno, če ne "
"uporabljate brskalnika, ki ga spletno mesto prepozna kot <quote>veljaven</"
"quote>, čeprav bo &konqueror;, če mu boste dali priložnost, zadovoljivo "
"deloval z veliko večino spletnih strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To overcome this problem you can change the browser identification "
"information that &konqueror; sends for specific sites or domains by "
"selecting the <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/useragent/\">Browser "
"Identification</ulink> module in the &systemsettings; category "
"<guilabel>Network</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Da bi odpravili težave, lahko spremenite identifikacijske informacije "
"brskalnika, ki jih &konqueror; pošlje za določeno spletno mesto ali domeno z "
"izbiro modula <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/useragent/\">Identifikacija "
"brskalnika</ulink> v &systemsettings; kategorija <guilabel >Omrežje</"
"guilabel >."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Problems with getting a web page to work properly may also be due to its use "
"of &Java; or JavaScript. If you suspect that this may be the case check that "
"they have been enabled in the <guilabel>Java &amp; JavaScript</guilabel> "
"section of the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Težave pri pravilnem delovanju spletne strani so lahko tudi posledica "
"uporabe &Java; ali JavaScript. Če sumite, da je temu tako, preverite, ali so "
"bili omogočeni v <guilabel>Java &amp; JavaScript</guilabel> v pogovornem "
"oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving and Printing Web Items"
msgstr "Shranjevanje in tiskanje spletnih elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are viewing a web page you can save it (or at least the basic "
"&HTML; or similar source text) to your local disk with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. If the page you are viewing uses frames, then you will also be "
"given the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Frame As…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option. <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click in "
"the frame you want to save first."
msgstr ""
"Ko si ogledujete spletno stran, jo lahko shranite (ali vsaj osnovni &HTML; "
"ali podobno izvorno besedilo) na lokalni disk z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če stran, ki si jo ogledujete, uporablja okvirje, "
"boste imeli tudi možnost <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani okvir kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"<mousebutton>Leva</mousebutton> kliknite na okvir, ki ga želite najprej "
"shraniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the page uses a background image, you can get and save that with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Background Image As…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option."
msgstr ""
"Če stran uporablja sliko ozadja, jo lahko dobite in shranite z možnostjo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani sliko ozadja "
"kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"But if what you really want is that glorious picture of the latest Ferrari, "
"then <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the image will give you a "
"drop-down menu with a <guimenuitem>Save Image As…</guimenuitem> option. Be "
"sure to respect the owner’s copyright, and ask for permission before using "
"any pictures saved this way for anything other than your own viewing "
"pleasure."
msgstr ""
"Če pa resnično želite tisto veličastno sliko najnovejšega Ferrarija, potem z "
"<mousebutton>desnim</mousebutton> klikom na sliko dobite spustni meni z "
"možnostjo <guimenuitem>Shrani sliko kot...</guimenuitem >. Bodite "
"prepričani, da spoštujete avtorske pravice lastnika in prosite za "
"dovoljenje, preden uporabite katero koli sliko, shranjeno na ta način, za "
"kar koli drugega kot za lasten užitek ob gledanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a link (which may be a "
"picture) and select <guimenuitem>Save Link As…</guimenuitem> from the pop up "
"menu the basic &HTML; or similar source text will be downloaded and saved on "
"your local disk."
msgstr ""
"Če <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete povezavo (ki je lahko slika) in "
"v pojavnem meniju izberete <guimenuitem>Shrani povezavo kot...</"
"guimenuitem>, se bo osnovni &HTML; ali podobno izvorno besedilo preneslo in "
"bo shranjeno na vaš lokalni disk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a link (which may be a picture) "
"and choosing <guimenuitem>Copy Link Address</guimenuitem> will copy the "
"&URL; of the link to the clipboard so you can then paste it into, say, an e-"
"mail to a friend telling her about this wonderful new site."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na povezavo (ki je lahko slika) in "
"izbira <guimenuitem>Kopiraj naslov povezave</guimenuitem> bo kopiral &URL; "
"povezave do odložišča, tako da jo lahko nato prilepite v, recimo, e-pošto "
"prijateljici, ki ji govori o tem čudovitem novem spletnem mestu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking on a picture and choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Image</guimenuitem> copies the &URL; of the picture to the "
"clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desni</mousebutton> klik na sliko in izbira "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj sliko</guimenuitem> kopira &URL; slike v odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Printing a copy of the page you are viewing is easily done with the Menubar "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem> option or with the "
"Toolbar <guiicon>Print</guiicon> button."
msgstr ""
"Tiskanje kopije strani, ki si jo ogledujete, je preprosto z menijsko vrstico "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <guimenuitem>Natisni okvir</guimenuitem > ali "
"z gumbom <guiicon>Natisni</guiicon> orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid "&FTP;"
msgstr "&FTP;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the earliest, and still perhaps "
"the best, way of transferring files between computers over the Internet."
msgstr ""
"&FTP;, File Transfer Protocol oziroma protokol za prenos datotek je eden "
"zgodnejših in verjetno je vedno najboljši način prenosa datotek na "
"računalnik v internetu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as if "
"they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
"&konqueror;’s normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> or Drag’n Drop methods and, if allowed, upload files from your "
"machine to the other computer’s filesystem. To try it, type the &URL;"
msgstr ""
"Z &FTP; Datoteke in mape na oddaljenem računalniku si lahko ogledate tako, "
"kot da bi bile v vašem sistemu, prenesite jih na svoj računalnik z običajno "
"metodo <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem> ali povleci v &konqueror;  nato z metode potegni in spusti in, "
"če je dovoljeno, naložite datoteke iz vašega računalnika v datotečni sistem "
"drugega računalnika. Če želite poskusiti, vnesite &URL;"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>ftp://ftp.l10n.kde.org</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>ftp://ftp.l10n.kde.org</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"into the Location Toolbar and press <keysym>Enter</keysym>. As long as you "
"are connected to the Internet, you should end up seeing the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ftp</filename> folder of the l10n server."
msgstr ""
"v orodno vrstico lokacije in pritisnite <keysym>Enter</keysym>. Dokler ste "
"povezani v internet, bi morali na koncu videti mapo <filename class="
"\"directory\">ftp</filename> strežnika l10n."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although, strictly speaking, &FTP; &URL;s should be entered starting with "
"<userinput>ftp://</userinput> and <acronym>WWW </acronym> &URL;s starting "
"with <userinput>http://</userinput> &konqueror; is usually smart enough to "
"figure out what is meant, and insert these characters for you if you leave "
"them out."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav, strogo gledano, &FTP; &URL;-je je treba vnesti začenši z "
"<userinput>ftp://</userinput> in <acronym>WWW </acronym> &URL;-je začenši z "
"<userinput>http://</userinput> &konqueror; je običajno dovolj pameten, da "
"ugotovi, kaj je mišljeno, in namesto vas vstavi te znake, če jih izpustite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you access an &FTP; site it will usually need some form of username and "
"password from you. To simplify things, most &FTP; sites that offer files for "
"free downloading will accept the word <systemitem class=\"username\"> "
"anonymous</systemitem> as a username and your email address as a password, "
"and to make your life even easier &konqueror; will automatically supply "
"these without troubling you."
msgstr ""
"Ko dostopate do &FTP; spletno mesto običajno od vas potrebuje neko "
"uporabniško ime in geslo. Za poenostavitev je večina &FTP; spletna mesta, ki "
"ponujajo datoteke za brezplačen prenos, bodo sprejela besedo <systemitem "
"class=\"username\"> anonimno</systemitem> kot uporabniško ime in vaš e-"
"poštni naslov kot geslo, in da bo vaše življenje še lažje, &konqueror; jih "
"bo samodejno zagotovil, ne da bi vas obremenjeval."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to access an &FTP; site that does not need a proper username or "
"password but which is too busy to accept any more connections, &konqueror; "
"often interprets the <quote>busy</quote> message as a request for a name and "
"password and will therefore pop up a dialog box asking you to supply them."
msgstr ""
"Če poskušate dostopati do &FTP; spletno mesto, ki ne potrebuje ustreznega "
"uporabniškega imena ali gesla, vendar je preveč zasedeno, da bi sprejelo več "
"povezav, &konqueror; pogosto razlaga sporočilo <quote>zasedeno</quote> kot "
"zahtevo po imenu in geslu, zato se prikaže pogovorno okno, ki vas prosi, da "
"ju vnesete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sites that are more concerned with security will need a proper username and "
"password, in which case &konqueror; will ask you for them or you can include "
"the username in the &URL; you type into the Location Toolbar, as for example"
msgstr ""
"Spletna mesta, ki se bolj ukvarjajo z varnostjo, bodo potrebovala ustrezno "
"uporabniško ime in geslo, v tem primeru &konqueror; vas bo vprašal zanje ali "
"pa vključite uporabniško ime v &URL; vnesete v orodno vrstico lokacije, kot "
"na primer"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ftp://<replaceable>username</replaceable>@ftp.l10n.kde.org</"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ftp://<replaceable>uporabniško ime</replaceable>@ftp.l10n.kde."
"org</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; will then prompt you for the password."
msgstr "&konqueror; vas bo nato vprašal za geslo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; can also support automatic logins as specified in a <filename>."
"netrc</filename> file. Details of how to enable this feature are given at "
"<ulink url=\"https://konqueror.org/faq/"
"#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles\"> https://konqueror."
"org/faq/#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; lahko podpira tudi samodejne prijave, kot je določeno v datoteki "
"<filename>.netrc</filename>. Podrobnosti o tem, kako omogočiti to funkcijo, "
"so na <ulink url=\"https://konqueror.org/faq/"
"#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles\"> https://konqueror."
"org/faq/#DoesKonquerorsupportautomaticftploginsvianetrcfiles</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL;s with Port Numbers"
msgstr "&URL; s številkami vrat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you specify a port number in your &URL;, as in for example "
"<userinput>http://intranet.corp.com:1080</userinput>, you might get the "
"error message <quote>Access to restricted port in POST denied</quote>. This "
"is done for security reasons. If you nevertheless need to access a server on "
"this port, just add a key line <screen><userinput>\n"
"OverridenPorts=CommaSeparatedListOfAllowedPorts\n"
"</userinput></screen> to <filename>kio_httprc</filename> in the folder "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation)</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če v svojem &URL; navedete številko vrat, kot je na primer <userinput>http://"
"intranet.corp.com:1080</userinput>, se lahko prikaže sporočilo o napaki "
"<quote>Dostop do omejenih vrat v POST zavrnjen </quote>. To se naredi iz "
"varnostnih razlogov. Če kljub temu potrebujete dostop do strežnika na teh "
"vratih, preprosto dodajte ključno vrstico <screen><userinput>\n"
"OverridenPorts=CommaSeparatedListOfAllowedPorts\n"
"</userinput></screen> v <filename>kio_httprc</filename> v mapi <filename "
"class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation)</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example <screen><userinput>OverridenPorts=23,15\n"
"</userinput></screen> (it should not include any embedded spaces)."
msgstr ""
"Na primer <screen><userinput>OverridenPorts=23,15\n"
"</userinput></screen> (ne sme vsebovati nobenih vdelanih presledkov)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; will reject the following ports:"
msgstr "&konqueror; bo zavrnil naslednja vrata:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15, 17, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 25, 37, 42, 43, 53, 77, 79, 87, "
"95, 101, 102, 103, 104, 109, 110, 111, 113, 115, 117, 119, 123, 135, 139, "
"143, 179, 389, 512, 513, 514, 515, 526, 530, 531, 532, 540, 556, 587, 601, "
"989, 990, 992, 993, 995, 1080, 2049, 4045, 6000, 6667"
msgstr ""
"1, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15, 17, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 25, 37, 42, 43, 53, 77, 79, 87, "
"95, 101, 102, 103, 104, 109, 110, 111, 113, 115, 117, 119, 123, 135, 139, "
"143, 179, 389, 512, 513, 514, 515, 526, 530, 531, 532, 540, 556, 587, 601, "
"989, 990, 992, 993, 995, 1080, 2049, 4045, 6000, 6667"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Text Completion"
msgstr "Samodejno dokončanje besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can get &konqueror; to help you enter a path or &URL; into the Location "
"Toolbar by enabling one of the <guimenuitem>Text Completion</guimenuitem> "
"features. To do this <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a clear part "
"of the Location Toolbar text entry box and select <guisubmenu>Text "
"Completion</guisubmenu> from the pop up menu. This will let you choose "
"between the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Lahko dobite &konqueror; za pomoč pri vnosu poti ali &URL; v orodno vrstico "
"lokacije tako, da omogočite eno od funkcij <guimenuitem>Dokončanje besedila</"
"guimenuitem>. To naredite z <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> klikom na "
"prazen del polja za vnos besedila orodne vrstice lokacije in v pojavnem "
"meniju izberite <guisubmenu>Dokončanje besedila</guisubmenu>. Tako boste "
"lahko izbirali med naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1582
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Nobeden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1583
#, no-c-format
msgid "What you get is what you type."
msgstr "Kar vtipkate, to dobite."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "Ročno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have typed part of a path or &URL;, pressing <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> or &Tab; will complete the "
"entry if it is possible to do so unambiguously."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste vnesli del poti ali &URL;, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> ali &Tab; bo vnos dopolnil, če bo to "
"mogoče nedvoumno storiti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "Avtomatsko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you type into the Location Toolbar window &konqueror; will automatically "
"extend what you type to complete one possible path or &URL;, highlighting "
"the characters it has added. Continue typing if that’s not what you wanted "
"or press <keysym>Enter</keysym> to accept it."
msgstr ""
"Ko tipkate v okno orodne vrstice lokacije &konqueror; bo samodejno razširil "
"tisto, kar vtipkate, da bo dokončal eno možno pot ali &URL;, pri čemer bo "
"poudaril znake, ki jih je dodal. Nadaljujte s tipkanjem, če to ni tisto, kar "
"ste želeli, ali pritisnite <keysym>Enter</keysym>, da ga sprejmete."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dropdown List"
msgstr "Spustni seznam"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A drop-down window will appear as you type, showing the possible matches to "
"what you have typed so far. When the path or &URL; that you want appears in "
"the window click on it with the &LMB;. You can also use the <keysym>Down</"
"keysym> or &Tab; and <keysym>Up</keysym> or <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo> keys to select it then press <keysym>Enter</"
"keysym>."
msgstr ""
"Med tipkanjem se prikaže spustno okno, ki prikazuje možna ujemanja s tem, "
"kar ste vnesli do zdaj. Ko je pot ali &URL; ki ga želite prikazati v oknu "
"kliknite nanj z &LMB;. Uporabite lahko tudi <keysym>Dol</keysym> ali &Tab; "
"in <keysym>Gor</keysym> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Tab;</"
"keycombo>, da jo izberete, nato pritisnite <keysym>Enter</keysym>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Short Automatic"
msgstr "Kratek avtomatski"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is like Automatic mode except that it only extends what you have typed "
"as far as the next <keycap>/</keycap> symbol in the path or &URL;. Press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> or &Tab; to "
"accept the suggestion, <keysym>Enter</keysym> when the complete path or "
"&URL; is shown."
msgstr ""
"To je kot samodejni način, le da razširi tisto, kar ste vnesli, do "
"naslednjega simbola <keycap>/</keycap> na poti ali &URL;. Pritisnite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> ali &Tab; da "
"sprejmete predlog, <keysym>Vnesite</keysym>, ko je vnesena celotna pot ali "
"&URL; je prikazano."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dropdown List &amp; Automatic"
msgstr "Spustni seznam &amp; Samodejno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a combination of both options described above."
msgstr "To je kombinacija obeh zgoraj opisanih možnosti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Privzeto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item appears at the bottom of the submenu and enables you to switch to "
"the default behaviour <guimenuitem>Dropdown List</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ta element se pojavi na dnu podmenija in vam omogoča, da preklopite na "
"privzeto vedenje <guimenuitem>Spustni seznam</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should try out these different modes and pick the one that suits you "
"best."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusite te različne načine in izberite tistega, ki vam najbolj ustreza."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bookmarks"
msgstr "Uporaba zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although you can use &konqueror;’s bookmarks to record the locations of your "
"own files and folders, they are most useful when you are surfing the Web, "
"letting you build up a list of useful sites."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav lahko uporabite zaznamke &konqueror; za beleženje lokacij lastnih "
"datotek in map, so najbolj uporabni, ko brskate po spletu, saj vam omogočajo "
"sestavljanje seznama uporabnih spletišč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> click on the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. Once the list "
"is visible, you can navigate through it with the arrow keys or with your "
"mouse, then press <keysym>Enter</keysym> or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click to visit the selected location."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti meni <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu>, <mousebutton>levo</"
"mousebutton> kliknite na meni <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu>. Ko je seznam "
"viden, se lahko po njem premikate s puščičnimi tipkami ali z miško, nato pa "
"pritisnete <keysym>Enter</keysym> ali <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> klik, "
"da obiščete izbrano lokacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new item to the list use <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> or <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on a clear space in the web page or folder view and "
"select <guimenuitem>Bookmark this Page</guimenuitem> from the pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite na seznam dodati nov element, uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Zaznamki </guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> ali <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknite na prazen "
"prostor v pogledu spletne strani ali mape in v pojavnem meniju izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj to stran med zaznamke</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> list can contain subfolders containing "
"other bookmarks, you can create these with <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New Bookmark Folder…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> To add "
"a bookmark into a subfolder rather than into the main Bookmark list, select "
"the folder from within the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> list and use the "
"<guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem> item in that folder."
msgstr ""
"Seznam <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> lahko vsebuje podmape z drugimi zaznamki, "
"ustvarite jih lahko z <menuchoice><guimenu>Zaznamki </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova mapa z zaznamki...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Če "
"želite dodati zaznamek v podmapo namesto na glavni seznam zaznamkov, "
"izberite mapo na seznamu <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> in uporabite element "
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</guimenuitem> v tej mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enter <userinput>bookmarks:</userinput> in the location bar the "
"bookmarks home page with an overview of all bookmarks and folders is shown."
msgstr ""
"Če v lokacijsko vrstico vnesete <userinput>zaznamki:</userinput>, se prikaže "
"domača stran zaznamkov s pregledom vseh zaznamkov in map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to edit your bookmarks use the <ulink url=\"help:/keditbookmarks/"
"index.html\">Bookmark Editor</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti svoje zaznamke, uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/"
"keditbookmarks/index.html\">urejevalnik zaznamkov</ulink>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Settings"
msgstr "Shranjevanje nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify different <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu settings for an "
"individual folder. To do this select <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Adjust View Properties…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, change the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> settings in the dialog to whatever you want. Then "
"apply the view properties to the <guilabel>Current folder</guilabel>. Doing "
"this creates a <filename>.directory</filename> file in that folder to hold "
"the folder <guimenu>View</guimenu> settings. Use this dialog again to remove "
"the folder specific settings (or just delete the <filename>.directory</"
"filename> file)."
msgstr ""
"Določite lahko različne nastavitve menija <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> za "
"posamezno mapo. Če želite to narediti, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi lastnosti pogleda...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, spremenite nastavitve <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> v pogovornem "
"oknu kakor želite. Nato uporabite lastnosti pogleda za <guilabel>Trenutno "
"mapo</guilabel>. S tem ustvarite datoteko <filename>.directory</filename> v "
"tej mapi, ki vsebuje nastavitve mape <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>. Znova "
"uporabite to pogovorno okno, da odstranite specifične nastavitve mape (ali "
"samo izbrišite datoteko <filename>.directory</filename>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One nice use of this feature is if you have a folder full of pictures, you "
"can set that particular folder to display thumbnails of the pictures (by "
"choosing the <menuchoice><guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Icons</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <guimenuitem>Preview</"
"guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu) when you open it, while "
"not displaying images as thumbnails in other folders."
msgstr ""
"Ena dobra uporaba te funkcije je, da če imate mapo, polno slik, nastavite to "
"posebno mapo za prikaz sličic slik (z izbiro <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Načina "
"pogleda</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ikone</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"<guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem> iz menija <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>), "
"ko ga odprete, medtem ko ne prikaže slik kot sličic v drugih mapah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1944
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Plugins</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vtičniki</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1947
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror; Plugins"
msgstr "&konqueror; Vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kde; releases several useful plugins that interact with &konqueror; in "
"various ways. These are explained briefly below."
msgstr ""
"&kde; izda več uporabnih vtičnikov, ki komunicirajo s &konqueror; na "
"različne načine. Ti so na kratko razloženi spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Extensions…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to open a dialog with all installed plugins and "
"select the ones you need. All plugins are accessible in the <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"razširitve...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno z vsemi "
"nameščenimi vtičniki in izberete tiste, ki jih potrebujete. Vsi vtičniki so "
"dostopni v meniju <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only plugins appropriate for the current mode (file manager or browser) are "
"listed in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Primerni so samo vtičniki za trenutni način (upravljalnik datotek ali "
"brskalnik).navedene v pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browser Mode"
msgstr "Način brskalnika"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1962
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Page Translation"
msgstr "Prevod spletne strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This uses the machine translation service provided by <ulink url=\"https://"
"translate.google.com/\">Google Translate</ulink> to translate the current "
"<acronym>HTML</acronym> page to whatever language you want (within reason). "
"It can be launched with <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Translate Web Page</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"To uporablja storitev strojnega prevajanja <ulink url=\"http://translate."
"google.com/\">Google Translate</ulink> za prevajanje trenutne strani "
"<acronym>HTML</acronym> v kateri koli jezik, ki ga želite (znotraj "
"razumnega). Zaženete ga lahko z <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Prevedi spletno stran</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a portion of the text on the page selected, that will be "
"translated instead of the entire &URL;."
msgstr ""
"Če imate izbran del besedila na strani, bo ta preveden namesto celotnega "
"&URL;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Machine translation is not a perfect science! Google will at best give you a "
"rough translation, and at worst will give you a very funny read. Don’t base "
"important decisions on things you have read from a Google translated page, "
"without confirming that the translation is indeed accurate."
msgstr ""
"Strojno prevajanje ni popolna znanost! Google vam bo v najboljšem primeru "
"dal približen prevod, v najslabšem primeru pa zelo smešno branje. Ne "
"sprejemajte pomembnih odločitev na podlagi stvari, ki ste jih prebrali na "
"strani, prevedeni z Googlom, ne da bi potrdili, da je prevod res točen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may only translate web pages that are accessible on the world wide web. "
"To translate any other text, you should go directly to the Google site "
"itself, where you are able to paste in text for translation."
msgstr ""
"Prevajate lahko samo spletne strani, ki so dostopne v svetovnem spletu. Če "
"želite prevesti katero koli drugo besedilo, pojdite neposredno na Googlovo "
"spletno mesto, kjer lahko prilepite besedilo za prevod."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1989
#, no-c-format
msgid "HTML Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve HTML"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>HTML Settings</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> to enable or disable a number of HTML settings "
"without going through the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavitve HTML</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>, da omogočite ali onemogočite številne nastavitve "
"HTML, ne da bi šli skozi pogovorno okno <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1994
#, no-c-format
msgid "JavaScript"
msgstr "JavaScript"

