#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directory Filter"
msgstr "Filter imenika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is controlled by <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Show Filter Bar</guisubmenu></menuchoice> and allows you "
"to choose which types of item are displayed in a folder."
msgstr ""
"To nadzira <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Pokaži Filtrirno vrstico</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in "
"vam omogoča, da izberete, katere vrste elementov so prikazane v mapi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Gallery"
msgstr "Galerija slik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In File Manager mode, you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Create Image Gallery</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or use "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> to create an HTML page with "
"thumbnails of all the images in the current folder. By default the HTML page "
"is called <filename>images.html</filename> and the thumbnails are put into a "
"new <filename>images</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"V načinu upravljalnika datotek lahko izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Ustvari galerijo slik</guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali "
"uporabite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo>, da ustvarite stran "
"HTML s sličicami vseh slik v trenutni mapi. Stran HTML se privzeto imenuje "
"<filename>images.html</filename>, sličice pa so postavljene v novo mapo "
"<filename>slike</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the Image Gallery plugin a dialog opens allowing you to "
"adjust the way the gallery is created."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete vtičnik Galerija slik, se odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko "
"prilagodite način ustvarjanja galerije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page Look"
msgstr "Pogled na stran"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2067
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Look dialog is for adjusting the appearance of the gallery page."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Pogled je namenjeno prilagajanju videza strani galerije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look Dialog Screenshot"
msgstr "Poglejte posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2077 index.docbook:2148 index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2085
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page title"
msgstr "Naslov strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Page title option has a text input box for changing the title of the "
"image gallery page."
msgstr ""
"Možnost Naslov strani ima polje za vnos besedila za spreminjanje naslova "
"strani galerije slik."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Images per row"
msgstr "Slike na vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Images per row option has a slider and a spin box for adjusting the "
"number of thumbnails that are in a single row in the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Možnost Slike na vrstico ima drsnik in vrtljivo polje za prilagajanje "
"števila sličic, ki so v eni vrstici v galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2095
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image file name"
msgstr "Pokaži ime slikovne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image file name check box allows you to choose whether to display "
"filenames below the gallery thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje Prikaži ime slikovne datoteke vam omogoča, da izberete, "
"ali želite prikazati imena datotek pod sličicami galerije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image file size"
msgstr "Prikaži velikost slikovne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image filesize check box allows you to choose whether to display "
"filesizes below the gallery thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje Prikaži velikost slikovne datoteke vam omogoča, da "
"izberete, ali želite prikazati velikosti datotek pod sličicami galerije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image dimensions"
msgstr "Prikaži dimenzije slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image dimensions check box allows you to choose whether to display "
