msgstr "Možnost Barva ozadja ima izbirnik za izbiro barve ozadja galerije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Mape"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Folders dialog is used for choosing where to save the gallery. This "
