#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image format for the thumbnails"
msgstr "Format slike za sličice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image format combo box allows you to choose which format is used for the "
"thumbnail images."
msgstr ""
"Kombinirano polje za format slike vam omogoča, da izberete, kateri format se "
"uporablja za sličice."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thumbnail size"
msgstr "Velikost sličice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The thumbnail size option provides a slider and spin box for adjusting the "
"size of the thumbnails used in the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Možnost velikosti sličic ponuja drsnik in vrtljivo polje za prilagajanje "
"velikosti sličic, ki se uporabljajo v galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set different color depth"
msgstr "Nastavi drugačno barvno globino"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The set different color depth check box enables a combo box for changing the "
"color depth of the thumbnails if you wish to use a different color depth to "
"that used in the original image."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje Nastavi drugačno barvno globino omogoča kombinirano polje "
"za spreminjanje barvne globine sličic, če želite uporabiti drugačno barvno "
"globino od tiste, uporabljene na izvirni sliki."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Bar"
msgstr "Iskalna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a text box for easy access to search engines such as Google. "
"Clicking on the icon on the left side of the search box opens a menu to "
"select and enable different search engines and configure their open the "
"<guilabel>Web Search Keywords</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja besedilno polje za preprost dostop do iskalnikov, kot je Google. "
"S klikom na ikono na levi strani iskalnega polja se odpre meni za izbiro in "
"omogočanje različnih iskalnikov ter konfiguracijo njihovih <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/webshortcuts/index.html\">spletnih bližnjic iskanja</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shell Command Plugin"
msgstr "Ukazni vtičnik lupine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin enables you to execute a shell command in the current folder and "
"view the output in a separate window."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik vam omogoča, da izvedete lupinski ukaz v trenutni mapi in si "
"ogledate izhod v ločenem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2264
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Mode Extensions"
msgstr "Razširitve načina pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; provides additional views in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in file manager and browser "
"mode, if the corresponding applications and plugins are installed."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; nudi dodatne poglede v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Način pogleda</guisubmenu></menuchoice> v načinu upravljalnika "
"datotek in brskalnika, če so nameščeni ustrezni programi in vtičniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file manager mode has the additional views <guimenuitem>Radial Map</"
"guimenuitem> from the application <application>Filelight</application> and "
"the &konqueror; plugin <guimenuitem>File Size View</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Način upravljalnika datotek ima dodatne poglede <guimenuitem>Radial Map</"
"guimenuitem> iz aplikacije <application>Filelight</application> in "
"&konqueror; vtičnik <guimenuitem>Pogled velikosti datoteke</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:2276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<personname><firstname>Josef</firstname> <surname>Weidendorfer</surname></"
"personname> <address><email>Josef.Weidendorfer@gmx.de</email></address>"
msgstr ""
"<personname><firstname>Josef</firstname> <surname>Weidendorfer</surname></"
"personname> <address><email>Josef.Weidendorfer@gmx.de</email></address>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid "&fsview;—the File System View"
msgstr "&fsview; - Pogled datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &fsview; Plugin for &konqueror; is another view mode for objects of "
"mimetype <literal>inode/directory</literal> for local files. It can be "
"viewed as an alternative to the various iconviews and listviews for browsing "
"the content of your local file system."
msgstr ""
"&fsview; Vtičnik za &konqueror; je še en način pogleda za objekte tipa mime "
"<literal>inode/directory</literal> za lokalne datoteke. Lahko si ga ogledate "
"kot alternativo različnim ogledom ikon in seznamov za brskanje po vsebini "
"vašega lokalnega datotečnega sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unique property of &fsview; is its ability to show whole nested folder "
"hierarchies using a so-called tree map for graphical visualization. Tree "
"maps allow for displaying metrics of objects in nested structures: each "
"object is represented by a rectangle whose area is proportional to its "
"metric. The sum of the children’s metrics must be equal to or smaller than "
"the parent object’s metric."
msgstr ""
"Edinstvena lastnost &fsview; je njegova zmožnost prikazati celotne ugnezdene "
"hierarhije map z uporabo tako imenovanega drevesnega pogleda za grafično "
"vizualizacijo. Drevesni pogledi omogočajo prikaz metrik objektov v "
"ugnezdenih strukturah: vsak objekt je predstavljen s pravokotnikom, katerega "
"površina je sorazmerna z njegovo metriko. Vsota metrik otrok mora biti enaka "
"ali manjša od metrike nadrejenega objekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &fsview;, sizes of files and folders are chosen as the metric, where the "
"size of a folder is defined to be the sum of the sizes of its subitems. This "
"way, big files even deep down in the folder hierarchy can be spotted easily "
"be looking for large rectangles. So &fsview; can be looked at as a graphical "
"and interactive version of the &UNIX; <command>du</command> command."
msgstr ""
"Za &fsview; so velikosti datotek in map izbrane kot metrika, pri čemer je "
"velikost mape definirana kot vsota velikosti njenih podpostavk. Na ta način "
"lahko velike datoteke, tudi globoko v hierarhiji map, preprosto opazite, če "
"iščejo velike pravokotnike. Torej &fsview; je mogoče obravnavati kot "
"grafično in interaktivno različico &UNIX; ukaza <command>du</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The integration of &fsview; as part of Konqueror allows it to use the "
"standard features such as context file menus, and mime type sensitive "
"actions. But it was chosen not to implement automatic update by watching "
"file system changes: if you delete a file shown in &fsview; outside of "
"&konqueror;, you have to update manually by &eg; pressing <keycap>F5</"
"keycap> to see the change. The reason for this decision is the potentially "
"huge number of files which would have to be watched for changes, and thus, "
"could put an unreasonable pressure on system resources for a small feature."
msgstr ""
"Integracija &fsview; kot del Konquerorja omogoča uporabo standardnih "
"funkcij, kot so kontekstni meniji datotek in dejanja, občutljiva na mime. "
"Vendar je bilo izbrano, da se ne izvede samodejna posodobitev z opazovanjem "
"sprememb datotečnega sistema: če izbrišete datoteko, prikazano v &fsview; "
"zunaj &konqueror;, morate posodobiti ročno z &eg; pritisnite <keycap>F5</"
"keycap>, da vidite spremembo. Razlog za to odločitev je potencialno ogromno "
"število datotek, ki bi jih bilo treba spremljati, da bi se spremenile, in bi "
"tako lahko povzročile nerazumen pritisk na sistemske vire zaradi majhne "
"funkcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Visualization Features"
msgstr "Funkcije vizualizacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section explains the graphical visualization of &fsview; in detail."
msgstr "Ta razdelek pojasnjuje grafično vizualizacijo &fsview; Podrobno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Item Drawing Options"
msgstr "Možnosti risanja predmeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &fsview;, an item of the tree map visualization is a rectangle "
"representing a file or folder of your file system. For easier navigation, "
"rectangles have meaningful coloring and labeling options."
msgstr ""
"V &fsview; je element vizualizacije drevesnega zemljevida pravokotnik, ki "
"predstavlja datoteko ali mapo vašega datotečnega sistema. Za lažjo "
"navigacijo imajo pravokotniki smiselne možnosti barvanja in označevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color of a rectangle, switchable via menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Color Mode</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> can be either representative of <guimenuitem>Depth</"
"guimenuitem>, for easy detection of nesting, or a color mapping of different "
"file attributes such as name, owner, group, or mime type."
msgstr ""
"Barva pravokotnika, ki jo lahko preklapljate prek menijskega elementa "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Barvni način</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>, je lahko predstavnik <guimenuitem>Globine</guimenuitem> za "
"enostavno zaznavanje gnezdenja ali barvno preslikavo različnih atributov "
"datoteke, kot so ime, lastnik, skupina ali tip mime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A rectangle can be labeled with the various attributes of the corresponding "
"file or folder. For each attribute, you can choose whether it should be "
"shown at all, only if space is available, or if space should be taken from "
"children (thus introducing errors to pure tree map drawing constraints). "
"Additionally, you can choose the relative location of the label in the "
"rectangle."
msgstr ""
"Pravokotnik je lahko označen z različnimi atributi ustrezne datoteke ali "
"mape. Za vsak atribut lahko izberete, ali naj bo sploh prikazan, le če je na "
"voljo prostor, ali če naj bo prostor vzet od podrejenih elementov (kar "
"povzroči napake v čistih omejitvah risanja drevesne karte). Poleg tega lahko "
"izberete relativno lokacijo oznake v pravokotniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2351
#, no-c-format
msgid "TreeMap Drawing Algorithms"
msgstr "Algoritmi za risanje TreeMap"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For drawing algorithms in tree maps, the rule that the area is proportional "
"to the metric of an item should hold true. With the tree map in &fsview;, "
"this goal isn’t always met: we draw borders to show the nesting of items, "
"and this border takes space for an item which is possibly lost for the areas "
"of child items. Note that less space is lost for the border if the rectangle "
"is quadratic."
msgstr ""
"Za risanje algoritmov v drevesnih pogledih mora veljati pravilo, da je "
"površina sorazmerna z metriko postavke. Z drevesnim pogledom v &fsview; ta "
"cilj ni vedno dosežen: narišemo obrobe, da pokažemo gnezdenje postavk, in ta "
"obroba zavzame prostor za postavko, ki je morda izgubljena za območja "
"podrejenih postavk. Upoštevajte, da se izgubi manj prostora za obrobo, če je "
"pravokotnik kvadraten."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, it is better for a good overview to let each rectangle at least "
"have its name as a label. It is an option to always force space for labels, "
"or only to draw labels when empty space is available. In the latter case, "
"the tool tips appearing when the mouse is held over an item can help a lot. "
"They show information for the item the mouse is currently over, together "
"with its parent folders up to the root item of the tree map."
msgstr ""
"Podobno je za dober pregled bolje, da ima vsak pravokotnik vsaj svoje ime "
"kot oznako. Obstaja možnost, da vedno vsilite prostor za oznake ali pa "
"narišete oznake samo, ko je na voljo prazen prostor. V slednjem primeru "
"lahko zelo pomagajo nasveti za orodje, ki se prikažejo, ko miško držite nad "
"elementom. Prikazujejo informacije za element, nad katerim je trenutno "
"miška, skupaj z njegovimi nadrejenimi mapami do korenskega elementa "
"drevesnega pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How the space of an item is split into subareas for children is left to the "
"implementation. It is always better to try to split areas in such a way that "
"rectangles are as quadratic as possible, both for labeling and less space "
"lost by borders. The best methods in this regard are <guilabel>Rows</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Columns</guilabel>, or <guilabel>Recursive Bisection</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Kako je prostor predmeta razdeljen na podobmočja za otroke, je prepuščeno "
"izvedbi. Vedno je bolje poskusiti razdeliti področja na tak način, da so "
"pravokotniki čim bolj kvadratni, tako zaradi označevanja kot zaradi manjše "
"izgube prostora zaradi obrob. Najboljše metode v zvezi s tem so "
"<guilabel>Vrstice</guilabel>, <guilabel>Stolpci</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Rekurzivna razpolovitev</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose the minimal area of items to be drawn via the menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop at Area</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Instead, a hash pattern will be drawn over the parents area to "
"signal that this space is in fact occupied by a child or children."
msgstr ""
"Z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustavi "
"se na območju</guimenuitem></menuchoice> lahko izberete najmanjšo površino "
"elementov, ki jih želite narisati. Namesto tega bo nad območjem staršev "
"narisan zgoščeni vzorec, ki signalizira, da ta prostor dejansko zasedajo "
"otrok ali otroci."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2386
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&fsview; supports multiple selection of items, similar to the iconview and "
"listview. This allows for actions to be done simultaneously to a set of "
"files. A simple mouse click always selects a single item below the mouse "
"pointer. Use a mouse click in combination with pressing the &Shift; key for "
"range selection or the &Ctrl; key for selection toggle. Note that by "
"selecting an item, subitems can no longer be selected. Selecting an item "
"will also clear the selection of all its parent items before."
msgstr ""
"&fsview; podpira večkratno izbiro elementov, podobno kot pogled ikon in "
"pogled seznama. To omogoča sočasno izvajanje dejanj z nizom datotek. "
"Preprost klik z miško vedno izbere en element pod miškinim kazalcem. "
"Uporabite klik miške v kombinaciji s pritiskom &Shift; tipka za izbiro "
"obsega ali &Ctrl; tipka za preklop izbire. Upoštevajte, da z izbiro postavke "
"ni več mogoče izbrati podpostavk. Če izberete element, boste počistili tudi "
"izbor vseh njegovih prejšnjih nadrejenih elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keyboard navigation is available in tree maps: use <keycap>Left Arrow</"
"keycap> and <keycap>Right Arrow</keycap> keys to move the current item "
"between siblings, and the <keycap>Up Arrow</keycap> and <keycap>Down Arrow</"
"keycap> keys to go up and down the nesting hierarchy. <keycap>Space</keycap> "
"selects the item; in conjunction with &Shift; does range selection; and with "
"the &Ctrl; key held down simultaneously, toggles selection of the current "
"item. Press <keycap>Return</keycap> to run the open action on the current "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Krmarjenje s tipkovnico je na voljo v drevesnih zemljevidih: uporabite tipki "
"<keycap>Puščica levo</keycap> in <keycap>Puščica desno</keycap> za "
"premikanje trenutnega elementa med brati in sestrami ter <keycap>Puščica "
"navzgor</keycap> in <keycap>Puščične tipke dol</keycap> za premikanje gor in "
"dol po hierarhiji gnezdenja. <keycap>Preslednica</keycap> izbere element; v "
"povezavi z &Shift; izbira obsega; in s tipko &Ctrl; istočasno držano tipko "
"preklopi izbiro trenutnega elementa. Pritisnite <keycap>Return</keycap>, da "
"zaženete dejanje odpiranja trenutnega elementa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2409 index.docbook:3626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2410
