#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &konqueror;"
msgstr "Konfiguracija &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In common with the rest of &kde;, &konqueror; is highly configurable, so you "
"can really get the look and feel that best fits your needs and wishes."
msgstr ""
"V skladu z ostalim &kde; je &konqueror; zelo nastavljiv, tako da lahko "
"dosežete videz in obnašanje, ki kar najbolj ustrezata vašim potrebam in "
"željam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &kde; is newly installed, &konqueror;’s window contains a Menubar, Main "
"and Location Toolbars and possibly a Bookmark Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ko &kde; je na novo nameščen, okno &konqueror; vsebuje menijsko vrstico, "
"glavno in lokacijsko orodno vrstico ter morda orodno vrstico zaznamkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For detailed information how to modify toolbars and shortcuts please read "
"the sections about <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config.html#toolbars"
"\">Toolbars</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config.html#shortcuts"
"\">Shortcuts</ulink> in the Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnejše informacije o spreminjanju orodnih vrstic in bližnjic "
"preberite razdelke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config.html#toolbars"
"\">Orodne vrstice</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/config.html "
"#shortcuts\">Bližnjice</ulink> v Osnovah."

