#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2503
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Seznam ukazov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The shortcut key combinations shown in this chapter are the default ones. "
"They can of course be changed."
msgstr ""
"Kombinacije bližnjičnih tipk, prikazane v tem poglavju, so privzete. Seveda "
"jih je mogoče spremeniti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special Shortcuts"
msgstr "Posebne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2511
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are some useful shortcuts that are not shown in any of the menus:"
msgstr "Obstaja nekaj uporabnih bližnjic, ki niso prikazane v nobenem meniju:"

#. Tag: keycap
#: index.docbook:2515
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F6</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F6</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2517 index.docbook:2593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the focus to the text entry box in the Location Toolbar."
msgstr "Nastavi fokus na polje za vnos besedila v orodni vrstici lokacije."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:2522
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>.</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>.</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate the next tab page."
msgstr "Aktivirajte naslednjo stran zavihka."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:2529
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2531
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate the previous tab page."
msgstr "Aktivirajte stran prejšnjega zavihka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2541
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menubar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that some menu entries only appear when they are applicable to the file "
"you currently have open in &konqueror;. For example, the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find…</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> item will not appear when you are viewing the contents of a "
"directory."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se nekateri menijski vnosi prikažejo le, če so uporabni za "
"datoteko, ki jo imate trenutno odprto v &konqueror;. Na primer, element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> ne bo prikazan, ko si ogledujete vsebino imenika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has different menu items in file manager and browser mode. Only "
"the items for these two modes are described in this chapter."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; ima različne elemente menija v načinu upravljalnika datotek in "
"brskalnika. V tem poglavju so opisani le elementi za ta dva načina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> is using embedded components (&kde; "
"Parts) such as &gwenview; for image viewing, &okular; for <acronym>PDF</"
"acronym> and &PostScript; documents &etc; the menu items from these "
"applications are merged into &konqueror;’s menu. Help for these additional "
"menu items you find in the handbook of the embedded application."
msgstr ""
"Če <emphasis>&konqueror;</emphasis> uporablja vdelane komponente (&kde; "
"Parts), kot je &gwenview; za ogled slik &okular; za <acronym>PDF</acronym> "
"in &PostScript; dokumente itd., so elementi menija iz teh aplikacij združeni "
"v meni &konqueror;. Pomoč za te dodatne elemente menija najdete v priročniku "
"vdelane aplikacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2559
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2570 index.docbook:3407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open another &konqueror; window."
msgstr "Odpri drug &konqueror; okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov zavihek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2581
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open another &konqueror; tab, containing a blank page."
msgstr "Odpri drug &konqueror; zavihek, ki vsebuje prazno stran."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Location…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri lokacijo...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open File…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri datoteko...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a file using the &kde; file dialog."
msgstr "Odprite datoteko z &kde; pogovorno okno datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2608
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sessions</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a submenu to save the current session (open tabs and windows) for easy "
"retrieval, manage sessions and switch to previously saved sessions."
msgstr ""
"Odprite podmeni za shranjevanje trenutne seje (odprtih zavihkov in oken) za "
"enostavno iskanje, upravljanje sej in preklop na predhodno shranjene seje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2617
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send Link Address…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji naslov povezave...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send an email containing a link to the current location."
msgstr "Pošlji e-pošto s povezavo do trenutne lokacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Send File…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pošlji datoteko...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2630
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send an email containing the selected file as an attachment."
msgstr "Pošlji e-pošto z izbrano datoteko kot prilogo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only applies if you are viewing a document or web page, uses the "
"<guilabel>Save As…</guilabel> dialog box to let you save a copy to your own "
"computer."
msgstr ""
"Velja le, če si ogledujete dokument ali spletno stran, uporablja pogovorno "
"okno <guilabel>Shrani kot...</guilabel>, da lahko kopijo shranite na svoj "
"računalnik."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Frame As…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani okvir kot...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <guimenuitem>Save As…</guimenuitem> but for use with a web site "
"that uses frames."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot <guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem>, vendar za uporabo s "
"spletnim mestom, ki uporablja okvirje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print."
msgstr "Natisni."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Frame</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Okvir za tiskanje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2666
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print selected frame of a Web page."
msgstr "Natisni izbrani ovir spletne strani."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2671
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open With</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri z</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a list of applications installed on the system associated with the "
"mimetype of the current URL."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže seznam aplikacij, nameščenih v sistemu, povezanih z mimetipom "
"trenutnega URL-ja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close down this instance of &konqueror;."
msgstr "Zapri ta primerek &konqueror;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2696
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some items in the Menubar <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu can also be found by "
"&RMB; clicking on a free area of a view."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere elemente v meniju menijske vrstice <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> lahko "
"najdete tudi z &RMB; s klikom na prosto območje pogleda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo: <replaceable>Action</"
"replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi: "
"<replaceable>Dejanje</replaceable> </guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sometimes lets you reverse a mistaken action."
msgstr "Včasih vam omogoča obrniti napačno dejanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2716
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puts selected item(s) into the clipboard. If you then paste the items they "
"will be moved from the original location to the new one."
msgstr ""
"Postavi izbrane elemente v odložišče. Če nato prilepite elemente, bodo "
"premaknjeni s prvotne lokacije na novo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy selected item(s) to the clipboard."
msgstr "Prepiši izbrane element(e) na odložišče."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Paste the clipboard content into the Location Bar, if the Location Bar has "
"the focus."
msgstr ""
"Prilepite vsebino odložišča v lokacijsko vrstico, če ima lokacijska vrstica "
"fokus."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste Clipboard "
"Contents…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste one File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste one Folder</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste x Items</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager "
"mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi vsebino "
"odložišča...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi eno datoteko</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi eno Mapo</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi x elementov</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Paste the currently copied/cut item(s) to the current folder. If the "
"clipboard does not contain files or folders, the clipboard contents (such as "
"text or image data) will be pasted into a new file."
msgstr ""
"Prilepite trenutno kopirane/izrezane elemente v trenutno mapo. Če odložišče "
"ne vsebuje datotek ali map, bo vsebina odložišča (kot so besedilni ali "
"slikovni podatki) prilepljena v novo datoteko."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects all text in an &HTML; page or in a text page being previewed, you "
"can then <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> it and <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> it into a text editor."
msgstr ""
"Izbere vse besedilo v &HTML; strani ali na besedilni strani, ki si jo "
"ogledujete, jo lahko nato <guimenuitem>kopirate</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>prilepite</guimenuitem> v urejevalnik besedila."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Create New</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Ustvari novo</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new object (such as a folder or a text file) in the current "
"folder. See the <link linkend=\"making\">Create New…</link> section for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov predmet (na primer mapo ali besedilno datoteko) v trenutni mapi. "
"Za več podrobnosti si oglejte razdelek <link linkend=\"making\">Ustvari "
"novo...</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>F2</keycap> </shortcut><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>F2</keycap> </shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you rename a file or folder without having to open the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties…</guimenuitem> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča preimenovanje datoteke ali mape, ne da bi morali odpreti pogovorno "
"okno <guimenuitem>Lastnosti...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Del</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager "
"mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>Del</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni v koš</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected item(s) to the Trash folder."
msgstr "Premakni izbrane elemente v mapo Smetnjak."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the selected item(s)."
msgstr "Izbriši izbrane(e) element(e)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit File Type…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi vrsto datoteke...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the <guilabel>Edit File Type</guilabel> dialog box"
msgstr "Odprite pogovorno okno <guilabel>Uredi vrsto datoteke</guilabel>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Properties…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti...</guimenuitem ></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika "
"datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2827
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the properties dialog for the currently selected item(s)."
msgstr "Prikaže pogovorno okno lastnosti za trenutno izbran(e) element(e)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select Items Matching…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izbira</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Izberi elemente, ki se ujemajo...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with the <guimenuitem>Unselect Items Matching…</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Unselect All</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Invert Selection</"
"guimenuitem> commands, this provides an easy and powerful way of selecting "
"multiple files."
msgstr ""
"Skupaj z ukazi <guimenuitem>Prekliči izbor elementov, ki se ujemajo...</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Prekliči izbor</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Obrni izbor</guimenuitem>, to zagotavlja enostaven in zmogljiv "
"način izbiranja več datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It brings up a simple dialog box where you can enter a file name using the "
"wild card characters * and ?, for example entering <literal role=\"extension"
"\">*.html</literal> will select all files ending with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.html</literal> while <filename>?a*</filename> will select all "
"files which have the letter a as the second character in their filename."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se preprosto pogovorno okno, kjer lahko vnesete ime datoteke z "
"uporabo nadomestnih znakov * in ?, na primer, če vnesete <literal role="
"\"extension\">*.html</literal>, boste izbrali vse datoteke, ki se končajo z "
"<literal role =\"extension\">.html</literal> medtem ko bo <filename>?a*</"
"filename> izbral vse datoteke, ki imajo črko a kot drugi znak v imenu "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Selection</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unselect Items Matching…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File "
"Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izbira</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prekliči izbiro elementov, ki se ujemajo...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unselect files or folders via a dialog similar to the one used by "
"<guimenuitem>Select…</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Prekliči izbor datotek ali map v pogovornem oknu, podobnem tistemu, ki ga "
"uporablja <guimenuitem>Izberi...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager "
"mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izbor</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem >Izberi vse</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika "
"datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects all items in a folder; you can then <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> them and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> "
"them into a different folder."
msgstr ""
"Izbere vse elemente v mapi; nato jih lahko <guimenuitem>Kopirate</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Izrežete</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Prilepite</guimenuitem> v drugo mapo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Selection</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unselect All</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izbira</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prekliči izbiro vseh</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unselect all selected files or folders."
msgstr "Prekliči izbiro vseh izbranih datotek ali imenikov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2881
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Selection</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Invert Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File "
"Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izbor</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Obrni izbor</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invert current selection."
msgstr "Obrni trenutno izbiro."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi...</"
"guimenuitem ></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the search bar at the bottom of the current window. Start typing to "
"find a text string in a text page you are previewing or in an &HTML; page."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže iskalno vrstico na dnu trenutnega okna. Začnite tipkati, da poiščete "
"besedilni niz na besedilni strani, ki si jo ogledujete, ali v datoteki "
"&HTML; strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2906
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2910
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Način pogleda...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In browser mode this submenu holds items to select embedded views like "
"<guimenuitem>WebEngine</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Embedded Advanced Text "
"Editor</guimenuitem> and more embedded views."
msgstr ""
"V načinu brskalnika ta podmeni vsebuje elemente za izbiro vdelanih pogledov, "
"kot je<guimenuitem>WebEngine</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Vdelan napredni "
"urejevalnik besedila</guimenuitem> in več vdelanih pogledov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In file manager mode this submenu holds items to select <guimenuitem>Icon</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Details</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Compact</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Terminal Emulator</guimenuitem> and more view "
"modes."
msgstr ""
"V načinu upravljalnika datotek ta podmeni vsebuje elemente za izbiro "
"<guimenuitem>Ikona</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Podrobnosti</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kompaktno</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Emulator terminala</"
"guimenuitem> in več načinov pogleda ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lock to Current Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zakleni trenutno lokacijo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A locked view cannot change folders. Use in combination with "
"<guimenuitem>Link View</guimenuitem> to explore many files from one folder."
msgstr ""
"Zaklenjen pogled ne more spreminjati map. Uporabite v kombinaciji z "
"<guimenuitem>Pogled povezave</guimenuitem> za raziskovanje več datotek iz "
"ene mape."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2933
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Link View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pogled povezave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Link current view to others in a multiple view window. A linked view follows "
"folder changes made in other linked views. This is especially useful with "
"different types of views, such as a folder tree with an icon view or "
"detailed view, and possibly a terminal emulator window."
msgstr ""
"Povežite trenutni pogled z drugimi v oknu z več pogledi. Povezan pogled "
"sledi spremembam mape v drugih povezanih pogledih. To je še posebej uporabno "
"pri različnih vrstah pogledov, kot je drevo map s pogledom ikon ali "
"podrobnim pogledom, in po možnosti okno terminalskega emulatorja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Esc;</shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Esc;</shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2958
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop load (particularly useful when web browsing)."
msgstr "Ustavi nalaganje (posebej uporabno kadar brskate po spletu)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>View Document "
"Source</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ogled vira "
"dokumenta</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2969
#, no-c-format
msgid "View document source text."
msgstr "Prikaži besedilo izvorne kode dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only available if you are viewing a document or &HTML; page."
msgstr "Na voljo samo, če si ogledujete dokument ali &HTML; strani."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>View Frame Source</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ogled vira okvirja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2979
#, no-c-format
msgid "View frame source text"
msgstr "Prikaži besedilo izvorne kode okvirja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only applies if you are viewing a web site that uses frames. Similar to "
"<guimenuitem>View Document Source</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Dosegljivo le, če si ogledujete spletno stran, ki uporablja okvirje. Podobno "
"<guimenuitem>Glej izvorno kodo dokumenta</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Actual Size</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>Zoom Text Only</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Zoom To DPI</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Dejanska velikost</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Povečaj samo besedilo</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem "
">Povečaj na DPI</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These menuitems offer different actions to modify the size of the items in "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Ti elementi menija ponujajo različna dejanja za spreminjanje velikosti "
"elementov na strani."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Encoding</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavi kodiranje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to choose the character encoding used to display &HTML; pages. "
"<guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem> is usually the best choice."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro kodiranja znakov za prikaz &HTML; strani. "
"<guimenuitem>Privzeto</guimenuitem> je običajno najboljša izbira."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sort By</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Razvrsti po</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3009
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Changes whether items are sorted</action> by <guimenuitem>Name</"
"guimenuitem> or other criteria described in <link linkend=\"dolphin-view-"
"information\">Information in the View</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremeni, ali so elementi razvrščeni</action> po <guimenuitem>Imenu</"
"guimenuitem> ali drugih merilih, opisanih v <link linkend=\"dolphin-view-"
"information\">Informacijah v pogledu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Descending</guimenuitem> reverses the sort order. "
"<guimenuitem>Folders First</guimenuitem> sorts folders before files."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Padajoče</guimenuitem> obrne vrstni red razvrščanja. "
"<guimenuitem>Najprej mape</guimenuitem> razvrsti mape pred datotekami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Additional Information</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays additional information</action> described in <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view-information\">Information in the View</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže dodatne informacije</action>, opisane v <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view-information\">Informacije v pogledu</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays a symbolic preview of the file contents </action> in the "
"different view modes."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže simboličen predogled vsebine datoteke </action> v različnih "
"načinih pogleda."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show in Groups</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži v skupinah</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the content of the current folder grouped by the "
"option selected in <guimenuitem>Sort By</guimenuitem> (only available in the "
"Icons view mode)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> vsebino trenutne mape, razvrščeno po možnosti, "
"izbrani v <guimenuitem>Razvrsti po</guimenuitem> (na voljo samo v načinu "
"pogleda ikon)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Hidden "
"Files</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži skrite "
"datoteke</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3049
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows all the hidden files and sub-folders within the current folder."
msgstr "Prikaže vse skrite datoteke in podmape v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Adjust View Properties…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi lastnosti "
"pogleda...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">View Properties Dialog</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Odpre <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">pogovorno okno lastnosti "
"pogleda</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3065
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Go Menu"
msgstr "Meni Go"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Up</keysym></keycombo> </"
"shortcut><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Gor</keysym></keycombo> </"
"shortcut><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Gor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go up a level in the folder hierarchy or select a folder in the hierarchy "
"from the submenu."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na raven višje v hierarhiji map ali v podmeniju izberite mapo v "
"hierarhiji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Left</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Levo</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go back to the previous view or select a previously visited item from the "
"submenu."
msgstr ""
"Vrnite se na prejšnji pogled ali izberite predhodno obiskan element v "
"podmeniju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Desno</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3098
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can only go forward if you’ve previously gone back."
msgstr "Naprej lahko greste le, če ste se že vrnili nazaj."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home Page</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Domača "
"stran</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Domača stran</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način brskalnika)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to your home page as defined on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> page of "
"the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na svojo domačo stran, kot je določeno na strani <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel> v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home "
"Folder</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Domača "
"stran</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Domača mapa</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika "
"datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Changes</action> to the users home folder, &eg;, /home/Peter/."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremembe</action> uporabniške domače mape, &npr;, /home/Peter/."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Applications</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Aplikacije</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the folder holding your applications."
msgstr "Odprite mapo, v kateri so vaše aplikacije."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Network Folders</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omrežne mape</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Network folders show up in a special location of &konqueror; and &dolphin; "
"called a virtual folder. You can find more information on how to use this "
"folder in the <ulink url=\"help:/knetattach/index.html\">KNetAttach "
"Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Omrežne mape so prikazane na posebnem mestu v &konqueror; in &dolphin; "
"imenovana navidezna mapa. Več informacij o uporabi te mape najdete v <ulink "
"url=\"help:/knetattach/index.html\">KNetAttach Handbook</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Trash</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Smetnjak</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open your <filename class=\"directory\">Trash</filename> folder."
msgstr "Odprite mapo <filename class=\"directory\">Trash</filename>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Autostart</guimenuitem></"
