msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycap>F4</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način "
"upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a &konsole; terminal window."
msgstr "Odprite &konsole; terminalsko okno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find File…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi datoteko..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the &kfind; application."
msgstr "Odpri program &kfind;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Select Remote Charset</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> (File Manager mode)"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izberite oddaljeni nabor "
"znakov</guisubmenu></menuchoice> (način upravljalnika datotek)"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Offers to choose the charset used by a remote connection manually."
msgstr "Ponuja ročno izbiro nabora znakov, ki ga uporablja oddaljena povezava."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have &konqueror; plugins installed there will be additional entries "
"in the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu. See the <link linkend=\"konq-plugin"
"\">&konqueror; Plugins</link> chapter for further details."
msgstr ""
"Če imate &konqueror; nameščenih vtičnikov bodo dodatni vnosi v meniju "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"konq-plugin"
"\">&konqueror; Vtičniki</link> za nadaljnje podrobnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; Settings menu items described in the <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals &konqueror; has these application specific "
"menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; Elementi menija z nastavitvami, opisani v poglavju "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Meni z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> v &kde; Osnove &konqueror; ima te menijske vnose za "
"posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Terminal Emulator</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži terminalski emulator</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a small text terminal view at the bottom of the main window."
msgstr "Odpre majhno terminalski pogled na dnu glavnega okna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Sidebar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži stransko "
"vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the display of the &konqueror; sidebar."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz stranske vrstice &konqueror; ja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Celozaslonski način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes &konqueror; to full screen mode, in which the &konqueror; window "
"takes up the whole screen, and does not have the usual window decorations. "
"To exit full screen mode, click on the <guiicon>Exit Full Screen Mode</"
"guiicon> icon on the toolbar, or press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe &konqueror; v celozaslonski način, v katerem &konqueror; okno "
"zavzema celoten zaslon in nima običajnih okenskih okraskov. Za izhod iz "
"celozaslonskega načina kliknite ikono <guiicon>Izhod iz celozaslonskega "
"načina</guiicon> v orodni vrstici ali pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Extensions…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj razširitve...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog with all installed plugins (&eg; from the KDE module "
"extragear) and allows you to select the ones you need. All plugins are "
"accessible in the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno z vsemi nameščenimi vtičniki (&npr;. iz modula KDE "
"extragear) in vam omogoča, da izberete tiste, ki jih potrebujete. Vsi "
"vtičniki so dostopni v meniju <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Spell Checking…</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj preverjanje "
"črkovanja...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the spell checking configuration dialog box, in which you can "
"change settings associated with spell checking in &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo preverjanja črkovanja, v katerem "
"lahko spremenite nastavitve, povezane s preverjanjem črkovanja v &konqueror;."

