"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Desno</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni zavihek "
"desno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the current tab one place right in the list of tabs."
msgstr "Premaknite trenutni zavihek eno mesto desno na seznamu zavihkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3487
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from standard &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items described in "
"the section <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help "
"Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals you will have the menu entry "
"<guimenuitem>&konqueror; Introduction</guimenuitem> to revisit the "
"introductory pages that you got when &konqueror; was first started."
msgstr ""
"Poleg standardnega &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, opisani v "
"razdelku <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Meni Pomoč</"
"ulink> programa &kde; Osnove boste imeli menijski vnos "
"<guimenuitem>&konqueror; Uvod</guimenuitem> za ponoven ogled uvodnih strani, "
"ki ste jih dobili, ko je &konqueror; se je prvič začelo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I run &konqueror; from another window manager?"
msgstr ""
"Lahko poganjam &konqueror; iz katerega drugega okenskega upravljalnika?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just install &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; and &konqueror;, and from your favorite "
"window manager, launch &konqueror;. It should work just fine, but if it "
"doesn’t (&kde; developers don’t test that case often), report it to <ulink "
"url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink> and try running "
"<application>kdeinit</application> before running &konqueror;; it usually "
"helps."
msgstr ""
"Samo namestite &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; in &konqueror; ter iz vašega "
"najljubšega upravljalnika oken zaženite &konqueror;. Moralo bi delovati v "
"redu, če pa ne (razvijalci &kde; tega primera ne testirajo pogosto), ga "
"prijavite na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs. kde.org</"
"ulink> in poskusite zagnati <application>kdeinit</application> preden "
"zaženete &konqueror;; ponavadi pomaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3525
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where does &konqueror; keep all its configuration data?"
msgstr "Kje shranjuje &konqueror; vse svoje nastavitvene podatke?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally in the <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</filename> folder (this may be <filename>~/.local/share</"
"filename> on your system, depending on how &konqueror; was installed). Don’t "
"alter these files unless you really know what you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno v mapi <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</filename> (to je lahko <filename>~/.local/share</"
"filename> v vašem sistemu, odvisno od tega, kako je bil &konqueror; "
"nameščen) . Ne spreminjajte teh datotek, razen če res veste, kaj počnete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your bookmarks are held in <filename class=\"directory\">konqueror/bookmarks."
"xml</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Vaši zaznamki so v <filename class=\"directory\">konqueror/bookmarks.xml</"
"filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cookies are held in <filename class=\"directory\">kcookiejar/cookies</"
"filename>"
msgstr ""
"Piškotki so shranjeni v <filename class=\"directory\">kcookiejar/cookies</"
"filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your history, as used for the auto-completion feature, is in "
"<filename>konq_history</filename> in the folder <filename class=\"directory"
"\">qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Vaša zgodovina, kot se uporablja za funkcijo samodokončanja, je v "
"<filename>konq_history</filename> v mapi <filename class=\"directory"
"\">qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the folder <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths "
"GenericConfigLocation</filename> the file <filename>konquerorrc</filename> "
"holds a whole lot of general configuration settings."
msgstr ""
"V mapi <filename class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericConfigLocation</"
"filename> datoteka <filename>konquerorrc</filename> vsebuje veliko splošnih "
"konfiguracijskih nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folder <filename class=\"directory\">kio_http/</filename> in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericCacheLocation</filename> contains "
"the browser cache."
msgstr ""
"Mapa <filename class=\"directory\">kio_http/</filename> v <filename class="
"\"directory\">qtpaths --paths GenericCacheLocation</filename> vsebuje "
"predpomnilnik brskalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any folder specific view settings are put into <literal role=\"extension\">."
"directory</literal> files in the individual folders."
msgstr ""
"Vse nastavitve pogleda, specifične za mapo, se dajo v datoteke <literal role="
"\"extension\">.directory</literal> v posameznih mapah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I clear out the history file?"
msgstr "Kako počistim datoteko zgodovine?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two <quote>histories</quote>:"
msgstr "Obstajata dve <quote>zgodovini</quote>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One is used for text completion in the Location Toolbar text entry box. To "
"clear this <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the text entry box and "
"select <guimenuitem>Clear History </guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ena se uporablja za dokončanje besedila v polju za vnos besedila orodne "
"vrstice lokacije. Če želite počistiti to <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton>, "
"kliknite polje za vnos besedila in izberite <guimenuitem>Počisti zgodovino </"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The other is the log of visited locations. Select <guimenuitem>Show History</"
"guimenuitem> in the menu <guimenu>Go</guimenu> and <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click on an entry and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Entry</"
"guimenuitem> (&Del;) to remove just that entry or <guimenuitem>Clear "
"History</guimenuitem> to delete all entries."
msgstr ""
"Drugi je dnevnik obiskanih lokacij. Izberite <guimenuitem>Pokaži zgodovino</"
"guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> in <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> kliknite na vnos in izberite <guimenuitem>Odstrani vnos</"
"guimenuitem> (&Del;) za odstranite samo ta vnos ali <guimenuitem>Počisti "
"zgodovino</guimenuitem>, da izbrišete vse vnose."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the application &sweeper; from the kdeutils module which "
"allows you to clean up cookies, favicons, web history and cache, form "
"completion entries and cache policies of visited websites."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi aplikacijo &sweeper; iz modula kdeutils, ki vam omogoča "
"čiščenje piškotkov, favikon, spletne zgodovine in predpomnilnika, vnosov za "
"dokončanje obrazcev in pravilnikov predpomnilnika obiskanih spletnih mest."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I enable, disable or clear the browser cache?"
msgstr "Kako omogočim, onemogočim ali počistim brskalnikov predpomnilnik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <menuchoice><guimenu>Web Browsing</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cache</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the dialog launched by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, you will be presented with a dialog box that lets "
"you disable the cache, clear it or set its size, and change the caching "
"policy."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Brskanje po spletu</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Predpomnilnik</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v pogovornem "
"oknu, ki se odpre z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Konqueror…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se "
"vam prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko onemogočite predpomnilnik, ga "
"počistite ali nastavite njegovo velikost in spremenite politiko "
"predpomnilnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I set my <quote>home</quote> page—the page loaded on startup?"
msgstr ""
"Kako nastavim svojo <quote>domačo</quote> stran - stran, ki se naloži ob "
"zagonu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has a <guilabel>Home Folder</guilabel> used in file manager mode "
"and a <guilabel>Home Page</guilabel> used in browser mode."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; ima <guilabel>Domačo mapo</guilabel>, ki se uporablja v načinu "
"upravljalnika datotek, in <guilabel>Domačo stran</guilabel>, ki se uporablja "
"v načinu brskalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change these settings launch <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Konqueror…</guimenuitem><guilabel>General</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti te nastavitve, zaženite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"Konqueror</guimenuitem><guilabel>Splošno</guilabel></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the &konqueror; startup page in filemanager mode select "
"<guilabel>Show Introduction Page</guilabel>, <guilabel>Show My Home Page</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Show Blank Page</guilabel> or <guilabel>Show My "
"Bookmarks</guilabel> from the drop down box labeled <guilabel>When Konqueror "
"starts</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti &konqueror; začetna stran v načinu upravljalnika datotek "
"izberite <guilabel>Pokaži uvodno stran</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pokaži mojo "
"domačo stran</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pokaži prazno stran</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Pokaži moje zaznamke</guilabel> iz spustnega menija <guilabel>Ko "
"se Konqueror zažene</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In browser mode &konqueror; starts with the <guilabel>Home page</guilabel> "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"V načinu brskalnika &konqueror; se začne z vnosom <guilabel>Domača stran</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid "I can’t find the answer to my question here."
msgstr "Tukaj ne najdem odgovora na svoje vprašanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find further information in the <ulink url=\"https://discuss.kde.org/"
"\"> KDE Community Forums</ulink> or on <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"Konqueror\"> Konqueror’s KDE Userbase page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne informacije lahko najdete v <ulink url=\"http://forum.kde.org/\"> "
"Forumih skupnosti KDE</ulink> ali na <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"Konqueror\" > Konquerorjeva stran KDE Userbase</ulink>."

